nTrackingID%3Dbiauto-61572-20%26h%3D56a2570ac491581d1755b4d8c5fad4092854b027c91be273e06e1f31e3fff5a0%26postID%3D64e77708458c1a6d3e1278b4%26postSlug%3Dguides%252Ftech%252Fgaming-laptop-vs-gaming-pc-desktop%26site%3Dbi%26u%3Dhttps%253A%252F%252Fwww.dell.com%252Fen-us%252Fshop%252Fdesktop-computers%252Falienware-aurora-r16-gaming-desktop%252Fspd%252Falienware-aurora-r16-desktop%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EAlienware%20R16%20desktop%3C%2Fa%3E%20and%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Faffiliate.insider.com%3FamazonTrackingID%3Dbiauto-61572-20%26h%3Df19b791cf795393216d20ad1f6491b1a15256420e94cfbe7c8c7cc8e0d4baaaf%26postID%3D64e77708458c1a6d3e1278b4%26postSlug%3Dguides%252Ftech%252Fgaming-laptop-vs-gaming-pc-desktop%26site%3Dbi%26u%3Dhttps%253A%252F%252Fwww.dell.com%252Fen-us%252Fshop%252Fdell-laptops%252Falienware-x16-gaming-laptop%252Fspd%252Falienware-x16-r1-laptop%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EAlienware%20x16%20laptop%3C%2Fa%3E%3A%20If%20you%20just%20look%20at%20the%20specs%20that%20Dell%20provides%2C%20you'll%20see%20that%20they're%20both%20configurable%20with%20an%20Intel%20i9%20CPU%20and%20RTX%204070%20GPU.%20But%20although%20these%20processors%20share%20the%20same%20basic%20model%20names%2C%20the%20desktop's%20parts%20and%20laptop's%20parts%20are%20actually%20different%3B%20the%20laptop%20is%20using%20a%20%26quot%3Bmobile%26quot%3B%20CPU%20and%20GPU%20that's%20smaller%20and%20weaker%20than%20the%20desktop's.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThere%20are%20three%20major%20reasons%20for%20this%20difference.%20The%20first%20is%20space%3A%20Desktop%20GPUs%20are%20massive%2C%20and%20can't%20fit%20inside%20of%20a%20small%20laptop%20frame.%20The%20second%20is%20power%3A%20Laptops%20have%20weaker%20power%20supplies%20than%20desktops%2C%20and%20can't%20support%20the%20wattage%20that%20desktop%20hardware%20needs.%20And%20the%20third%20is%20temperature%3A%20Laptops%20need%20to%20account%20for%20heat%20in%20a%20smaller%20area%2C%20so%20they%20use%20