%20Asus%20ROG%20Zephyrus%20G14%2C%20showing%20the%20home%20screen%20for%20the%20game%20Grand%20Theft%20Auto%20V%2C%20sitting%20on%20a%20green%20table%20in%20front%20of%20a%20fountain.%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F64cd382af5d4870019e1def0%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%222100%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EGaming%20laptops%20let%20you%20take%20your%20favorite%20games%20on%20the%20go.%3Cp%3EWilliam%20Antonelli%2FInsider%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20absolute%20biggest%20reason%20to%20buy%20a%20laptop%20is%20that%20it%20lets%20you%20bring%20your%20games%2C%20files%2C%20and%20apps%20wherever%20you%20go.%20You%20don't%20have%20to%20worry%20about%20carrying%20a%20separate%20screen%2C%20keyboard%2C%20or%20mouse%20either.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EBut%20while%20laptops%20are%20portable%2C%20%3Cem%3Egaming%3C%2Fem%3E%20laptops%20are%20less%20portable%20than%20normal%20ones.%20Since%20they%20have%20to%20hold%20bigger%2C%20more%20powerful%20hardware%2C%20gaming%20laptops%20are%20chunkier%20and%20heavier.%20That%20hardware%20also%20requires%20more%20power%2C%20which%20means%20heavier%20chargers%20and%20shorter%20battery%20life.%20In%20many%20cases%2C%20gaming%20laptops%20are%20more%20portable%20in%20theory%20than%20in%20practice.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fguides%2Ftech%2Facer-nitro-5-laptop-review%5C%22%3EAcer%20Nitro%205%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20for%20example%2C%20is%20a%20great%20budget%20gaming%20laptop%2C%20but%20it's%20so%20big%20that%20I%20rarely%20wanted%20to%20take%20it%20anywhere.%20And%20in%20contrast%2C%20the%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fguides%2Ftech%2Fasus-rog-zephyrus-g14-laptop-review%5C%22%3EAsus%20ROG%20Zephyrus%20G14%3C%2Fa%3E%20is%20one%20of%20my%20favorite%20laptops%20ever%20because%20of%20how%20uniquely%20portable%20it%20is.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EIn%20comparison%2C%20desktops%20are%20designed%20to%20stay%20in%20one%20place%20for%20long%20stretches%20of%20time%20%E2%80%94%20often%20forever.%20And%20no%20matter%20where%20you%20bring%20them%2C%20you'll%20need%20a%20power%20outlet%20to%20plug%20them%20into%2C%20along%20with%20external%20hardware%20like%20a%20monitor.%20This%20means%20it's%20pretty%20much%20impossible%20to%20use%20a%20desktop%20outside%20or%20in%20transit.%20Some%20brands%2C%20like%20Asus%2C%20do%20sell%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Frog.asus.com%2Fus%2Fdesktops%2Fsmall-form-factor%2Frog-g22ch-series%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Ecompact%20gaming%20desktop%20towers%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20but%20they're%20still%20much%20bulkier%20than%20a%20laptop%20and%20don't%20have%20built-in%20displays.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-label%3D%5C%22Heat%5C%22%3E%3Cstrong%3EGaming%20laptop%20vs.%20desktop%3A%20Heat%20and%20required%20power%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3EAnyone%20who's%20ever%20played%20on%20a%20gaming%20laptop%20(or%20even%20a%20regular%20laptop)%20is%20familiar%20with%20the%20burning%20sensation%20of%20a%20laptop%20chassis%20on%20their%20thighs.%20It's%20easy%20to%20assume%20that%20since%20they've%20got%20less%20open%20spaces%2C%20laptops%20run%20hotter%20than%20desktops.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20reality%20is%20a%20little%20more%20complicated.%20Laptop%20heat%20is%20definitely%20easier%20to%20notice%20since%20that%20heat%20is%20gathered%20in%20a%20smaller%20area%2C%20and%20you're%20usually%20touching%20the%20device%20directly.%20And%20since%20laptops%20can't%20dissipate%20heat%20as%20effectively%20as%20a%20desktop%2C%20they%20can%20run%20hotter%20when%20under%20heavy%20load.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EBut%20desktops%20use%20more%20power%2C%20and%20more%20power%20means%20hotter%20hardware.%20Over%20time%2C%20a%20gaming%20desktop%20is%20almost%20always%20going%20to%20generate%20more%20heat%20than%20a%20laptop%20will%2C%20even%20if%20that%20heat%20is%20managed%20better.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EAnd%20if%20you%20keep%20your%20desktop%20tower%20in%20a%20spot%20where%20it's%20going%20to%20gather%20dust%2C%20like%20under%20your%20desk%20or%20against%20a%20wall%2C%20it'll%20get%20even%20hotter.%20That's%20why%20desktop%20towers%20need%20more%20ventilation%20and%20bigger%20fans%2C%20and%20why%20it's%20vital%20to%20clean%20your%20desktop's%20vents%20regularly.%20Some%20gaming%20desktops%20can%20also%20support%20%26quot%3Bliquid%20cooling%26quot%3B%20systems%2C%20where%20a%20sealed%20block%20of%20fluid%20inside%20the%20case%20helps%20take%20heat%20away%20from%20the%20other%20parts.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-label%3D%5C%22Customization%5C%22%3E%3Cstrong%3EGaming%20laptop%20vs.%20desktop%3A%20Customization%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3E%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cfigure%3E%3Cstrong%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%222666%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22An%20AMD%20Ryzen%209%20CPU%20being%20set%20into%20a%20gaming%20PC.%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F64e77a48a7adf700190718ce%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%222000%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EGaming%20desktops%20are%20almost%20entirely%20modular.%3Cp%3ETester128%2FShutterstock%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20hardware%20inside%20desktop%20towers%20is%20far%20more%20customizable%20than%20the%20hardware%20inside%20laptops.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EWith%20gaming%20laptops%2C%20you%20can%20generally%20only%20switch%20out%20the%20RAM%20and%20storage.%20Everything%20else%20is%20soldered%20in%2C%20which%20means%20it%20can't%20be%20replaced.%20Additionally%2C%20the%20%26quot%3Bmobile%26quot%3B%20hardware%20that%20laptops%20use%20is%20generally%20harder%20and%20more%20expensive%20to%20buy.%20There's%20a%20reason%20why%20building%20a%20custom%20laptop%20is%20nigh%20unheard%20of%3A%20It's%20a%20tedious%20and%20costly%20task%20with%20no%20real%20reward.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20only%20real%20ways%20to%20customize%20a%20laptop%20are%20by%20using%20the%20laptop%20manufacturer's%20website%20before%20you%20buy%20it%2C%20and%20by%20attaching%20external%20accessories%20like%20a%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fguides%2Ftech%2Fbest-keyboard%5C%22%3Egreat%20keyboard%3C%2Fa%3E%20or%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fguides%2Ftech%2Fbest-gaming-mouse-pad%5C%22%3Ecool%20mousepad%3C%2Fa%3E.%20Depending%20on%20the%20brand%2C%20you%20might%20also%20be%20able%20to%20buy%20skins%20and%20faceplates%20to%20change%20how%20the%20exterior%20looks%20too.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EGaming%20desktops%2C%20meanwhile%2C%20are%20essentially%20a%20giant%20Lego%20kit.%20As%20long%20as%20the%20pieces%20are%20compatible%20and%20you%20have%20the%20right%20power%20supply%2C%20you%20can%20change%20out%20a%20desktop's%20CPU%2C%20GPU%2C%20RAM%2C%20motherboard%2C%20storage%2C%20and%20even%20the%20tower%20casing%20itself.%20You%20can%20build%20a%20desktop%20from%20scratch%2C%20and%20keep%20it%20running%20for%20years%20by%20gradually%20replacing%20and%20upgrading%20its%20parts%2C%20Ship%20of%20Theseus-style.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20ability%20to%20build%20a%20desktop%20PC%20from%20the%20ground%20up%20%E2%80%94%20a%20hobby%20that's%20become%20increasingly%20popular%20in%20the%20last%20few%20years%2C%20as%20evidenced%20by%20the%20explosive%20growth%20of%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.reddit.com%2Fr%2Fbuildapc%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EReddit's%20r%2Fbuildapc%20community%3C%2Fa%3E%20%E2%80%94%20also%20reduces%20the%20cost%20for%20a%20top-tier%20gaming%20computer.%20It's%20generally%20cheaper%20to%20buy%20computer%20parts%20individually%20than%20in%20a%20prebuilt%20machine.%20You'll%20just%20need%20patience%20and%20steady%20hands.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-label%3D%5C%22Price%5C%22%3E%3Cstrong%3EGaming%20laptop%20vs.%20desktop%3A%20Price%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3EFor%20the%20same%20amount%20of%20performance%2C%20gaming%20desktops%20are%20cheaper%20than%20gaming%20laptops.%20Take%20the%20example%20I%20brought%20up%20above%2C%20comparing%20the%20Alienware%20R16%20desktop%20and%20x16%20laptop%3A%20Despite%20having%20weaker%20mobile%20hardware%2C%20the%20x16%20laptop%20is%20more%20than%20an%20R16%20desktop%20with%20the%20same%20listed%20specs.%20When%20it%20comes%20to%20gaming%20laptops%2C%20you%20pay%20for%20the%20portability.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EHowever%2C%20if%20you're%20purchasing%20a%20gaming%20desktop%2C%20remember%20that%20you'll%20need%20to%20buy%20the%20external%20equipment%20too%2C%20like%20your%20monitor%2C%20speakers%2C%20and%20keyboard.%20Some%20manufacturers%20offer%20deals%20if%20you%20buy%20those%20accessories%20at%20the%20same%20time%20you%20buy%20your%20desktop%2C%20but%20with%20a%20laptop%20you%20get%20all%20of%20these%20essentials%20built%20into%20the%20device.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EIn%20general%2C%20whether%20you%20buy%20a%20desktop%20or%20laptop%2C%20gaming%20PCs%20are%20separated%20into%20three%20different%20price%20brackets%3A%20Budget%2C%20midrange%2C%20and%20high-end.%20Budget%20ranges%20from%20about%20%24600%20to%20%241%2C300%2C%20midrange%20goes%20from%20%241%2C400%20to%20%242%2C200%2C%20and%20high-end%20options%20will%20cost%20more%20than%20that.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-label%3D%5C%22Which%20should%20you%20buy%3F%5C%22%3E%3Cstrong%3EShould%20you%20buy%20a%20gaming%20laptop%20or%20desktop%3F%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3E%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cfigure%3E%3Cstrong%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%222100%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22A%20woman%20playing%20a%20shooting%20game%20on%20a%20gaming%20PC.%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F64e77ae2a7adf70019071a10%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%221575%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EGaming%20desktops%20offer%20the%20biggest%20bang%20for%20your%20buck.%3Cp%3EDC%20Studio%2FShutterstock%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3EIf%20you're%20looking%20at%20pure%20value%20%E2%80%94%20trying%20to%20get%20the%20best%20performance%20per%20dollar%20spent%20%E2%80%94%20then%20a%20gaming%20desktop%20is%20the%20clear%20choice.%20Purchasing%20a%20separate%20monitor%20and%20other%20accessories%20will%20ultimately%20add%20to%20your%20total%20costs%2C%20but%20from%20a%20gaming%20hardware%20perspective%2C%20you%20simply%20get%20more%20power%20for%20your%20money%20with%20a%20desktop.%20This%20is%20true%20whether%20you%20build%20your%20own%20PC%20or%20buy%20a%20pre-built%20model.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EEven%20if%20two%20machines%20have%20the%20same%20%3Cem%3Elisted%3C%2Fem%3E%20specs%2C%20desktop%20hardware%20is%20far%20more%20powerful%20than%20mobile%20laptop%20hardware.%20The%20only%20way%20to%20play%20games%20at%204K%20or%208K%20resolution%20with%20high%20graphical%20settings%20and%20steady%20framerates%20is%20with%20a%20gaming%20desktop.%20They're%20also%20great%20for%20intensive%20creative%20work%20in%20apps%20like%20Blender%2C%20and%20they're%20a%20must%20for%20livestreaming%20high-end%20games.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EIf%20you%20want%20a%20portable%2C%20all-in-one%20gaming%20and%20work%20computer%20(whether%20that's%20for%20a%20job%20or%20school)%2C%20then%20gaming%20laptops%20are%20great.%20They%20give%20you%20easy%20access%20to%20all%20your%20favorite%20games%2C%20but%20also%20give%20you%20the%20freedom%20to%20take%20your%20games%20and%20files%20wherever%20you%20go.%20I%20like%20traveling%20with%20my%20computer%2C%20so%20I've%20used%20a%20gaming%20laptop%20as%20my%20sole%20PC%20for%20years.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EAssuming%20you're%20starting%20from%20scratch%2C%20the%20best%20way%20to%20strike%20a%20balance%20between%20value%20and%20convenience%20is%20probably%20to%20buy%20a%20great%20gaming%20desktop%2C%20and%20then%20a%20budget%20gaming%20laptop%20you%20can%20travel%20with%20and%20play%20simpler%20or%20cloud-based%20games%20on.%20But%20if%20you%20have%20to%20pick%20one%2C%20it's%20hard%20to%20beat%20the%20value%20and%20power%20of%20a%20gaming%20desktop.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cdiv%3ERead%20the%20original%20article%20on%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinside