of%20Ramaswamy%20before%20he%20took%20the%20stage.%20After%20the%20debate%2C%20the%20poll%20found%2C%2026%25%20of%20potential%20primary%20voters%20who%20watched%20the%20debate%20rated%20Ramaswamy%20the%20winner%2C%20behind%20only%20DeSantis.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EBut%20it%20wasn't%20all%20good%20news%3A%20That%20%26quot%3Bunfavorable%26quot%3B%20number%20more%20than%20doubled%20to%2032%25%2C%20according%20to%20the%20same%20polling%20group.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThroughout%20the%20debate%2C%20Ramaswamy%20jumped%20in%20as%20often%20as%20he%20could%2C%20seizing%20the%20second-largest%20portion%20of%20speaking%20time%2C%20according%20to%20the%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.nytimes.com%2Finteractive%2F2023%2F08%2F23%2Fus%2Fpolitics%2Frepublican-debate-live-tracker.html%5C%22%3ENew%20York%20Times.%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EIn%20addition%20to%20discussing%20his%20policy%20plans%2C%20Ramaswamy%20used%20much%20of%20that%20time%20to%20directly%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Framaswamy-spends-first-gop-debate-attacking-nearly-everyone-but-trump-2023-8%5C%22%3Eattack%20the%20candidates%20around%20him%3C%2Fa%3E%20for%20their%20experience%20and%20records%20in%20office%3A%20He%20said%20former%20New%20Jersey%20Gov.%20Chris%20Christie%20was%20auditioning%20for%20an%20MSNBC%20contributor%20position%2C%20told%20former%20South%20Carolina%20Gov.%20Nikki%20Haley%20her%20future%20was%20in%20defense%20contracting%20instead%20of%20the%20White%20House%2C%20and%20mocked%20former%20Vice%20President%20Mike%20Pence%20about%20his%20age.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20other%20candidates%2C%20however%2C%20didn't%20let%20Ramaswamy%20simply%20get%20away%20with%20his%20repeated%20attacks%20on%20the%20debate%20stage.%20Instead%2C%20they%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Ftakeaways-first-republican-presidential-debate-trump-vivek-desantis-2023-8%5C%22%3Esingled%20him%20out%3C%2Fa%3E%20over%20his%20lack%20of%20political%20experience%20and%20radical%20for