Union%20leaders%20say%20they%20are%20calling%20for%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.seiu-uhw.org%2Fkaiser-campaign-updates%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Eincreased%20staffing%20to%20protect%20patients%3C%2Fa%3E%20and%20workers%20alike%2C%20a%20raise%20in%20pay%20differentials%20for%20evening%20and%20night%20shifts%2C%20and%20stability%20for%20remote%20workers.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BIf%20Kaiser%20does%20not%20come%20correct%20in%20the%20next%2045%20days%20or%20so%20before%20the%20expiration%20of%20this%20agreement%2C%20there%20will%20be%20a%20nationwide%20strike%20and%20that%20will%20be%20something%20that%20is%20avoidable%2C%26quot%3B%20Regan%20said.%20%26quot%3BIt%20would%20be%20a%20tragedy.%20It%20is%20not%20what%20this%20workforce%20wants%20to%20do%2C%20but%20it%20is%20what%20we%20are%20being%20left%20no%20choice%20to%20do.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EWayne%20Davis%2C%20a%20spokesperson%20for%20Kaiser%20Permanente%2C%20told%20Insider%20that%20union%20members%20should%20reject%20the%20call%20to%20strike.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BWe%20take%20any%20threat%20to%20disrupt%20care%20for%20our%20members%20seriously%20and%20have%20plans%20to%20ensure%20continued%20access%20to%20healthcare%20by%20our%20members%2C%20patients%2C%20and%20the%20communities%20we%20serve%2C%20should%20any%20union%20call%20for%20a%20strike%2C%26quot%3B%20Davis%20wrote.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EUnion%20representatives%20said%20they%20understood%20that%20a%20strike%20would%20affect%20patient%20healthcare%20but%20that%20staffing%20issues%20at%20the%20company%20were%20already%20negatively%20affecting%20patients%20%E2%80%94%20and%20workers.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BA%20strike%20would%20cause%20delays.%20But%20do%20you%20know%20what%20else%20causes%20delays%20in%20patient%20care%3F%20Not%20having%20the%20staff%20to%20treat%20the%20patients%20waiting%20six%20months%20in%20Colorado%20for%20a%20radiology%20appointment.%20That%20causes%20delays%20in%20care%2C%26quot%3B%20Caroline%20Lucas%2C%20executive%20director%20of%20the%20Coalition%2C%20said%20at%20the%20press%20conference.%20%26quot%3BWe%20would%20go%20on%20strike%20because%20we%20care%20about%20fixing%20those%20things.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20strike%20would%20happen%20on%20the%20grounds%20of%20unfair%20labor%20practices%2C%20including%20Kaiser%20Permanente's%20failure%20to%20bargain%20in%20good%20faith%20and%20failure%20to%20provide%20relevant%20information%20as%20required%20by%20law%2C%20Regan%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EDavis%20said%20these%20reports%20are%20%26quot%3Bunfounded.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BWe%20remain%20committed%20to%20bargaining%20with%20our%20Coalition%20unions%20in%20good%20faith%20and%20in%20the%20spirit%20of%20partnership%2C%26quot%3B%20Davis%20wrote.%20%26quot%3BWe%20will%20focus%20our%20energy%20on%20frank%20and%20productive%20discussions%20that%20lead%20to%20an%20agreement%2C%20and%20to%20doing%20our%20part%20to%20ensure%20there%20are%20no%20disruptions%20to%20the%20high-quality%20care%20we%20provide.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EOrganizers%20say%20that%20ever%20since%20the%20COVID-19%20pandemic%20began%2C%20healthcare%20workers%20have%20been%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fhealthcare-workers-nurses-long-covid-impact-careers-labor-shortage-2022-5%5C%22%3Eunder%20immense%20strain%20because%20of%20limited%20staffing%3C%2Fa%3E%20%E2%80%94%20and%20it%20isn't%20getting%20better.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ELiz%20Grigsby%2C%20a%20respiratory%20therapist%20and%20union%20member%2C%20said%20memories%20of%20patient%20deaths%20due%20to%20staffing%20shortages%20haunt%20her.%20She%20spoke%20about%20one%20patient%20in%20particular%2C%20a%20mother%20battling%20COVID-19%20after%20giving%20birth.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BI%20made%20a%20promise%20to%20her%20to%20stay%20by%20her%20side%20to%20come%20back%20and%20to%20provide%20the%20support%20she%20desperately%20needed%2C%20but%20the%20painful%20reality%20of%20short%20staffing%20prevented%20me%20for%20fulfilling%20that%20promise%2C%26quot%3B%20Grigsby%20said%20at%20the%20press%20conference.%20%26quot%3BWhen%20I%20came%20back%2C%20she%20already%20died.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EDavis%20says%20the%20company%20has%20worked%20with%20the%20Coalition%20to%20accelerate%20hiring%2C%20and%20that%20they%20have%20already%20filled%206%2C500%20positions.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ECatherine%20Engler%2C%20a%20licensed%20vocational%20nurse%20and%20union%20member%2C%20said%20patients%20are%20slipping%20through%20the%20cracks%20as%20staffing%20shortages%20continue.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BI%20lie%20awake%20at%20night%20wondering%20if%20I%20did%20everything%20I'm%20supposed%20to%20for%20both%20my%20family%20and%20my%20patients%2C%26quot%3B%20Engler%20said%20at%20the%20press%20conference.%20%26quot%3BIt%20scares%20me%20that%20we%20don't%20have%20enough%20staff.%20Healthcare%20workers%20are%20leaving%20the%20industry%20because%20they%20can't%20take%20it%20anymore%2C%20making%20the%20existing%20short-staff%20crisis%20worse%20and%20hurting%20our%20patients.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cdiv%3ERead%20the%20original%20article%20on%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fkaiser-permanente-healthcare-workers-union-strike-vote-labor-reform-covid-2023-8%5C%22%3EBusiness%20Insider%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1692907813000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F64e7ad0a52bc2d00199196b7%3Fformat%3Djpeg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fkaiser-permanente-healthcare-workers-union-strike-vote-labor-reform-covid-2023-8%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22The%20union%20strike%20would%20impact%20dozens%20of%20Kaiser%20Permanente%20facilities%20across%20seven%20states%20and%20Washington%2C%20DC%2C%20affecting%20millions%20of%20patients.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22khawkinson%40insider.com%20(Katie%20Hawkinson%20)%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A44%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fkaiser-permanente-healthcar