rs%2C%20like%20Mint%20and%20Lilac%2C%20which%20sets%20the%20G305%20apart%20from%20your%20average%20black-and-neon%20gaming%20mouse.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThough%20definitely%20not%20an%20ultralight%20mouse%2C%20the%20G305%20is%20fairly%20lightweight%20at%20only%2099%20grams.%20It's%20a%20good%20medium%20for%20casual%20gamers%3A%20not%20so%20light%20that%20your%20cursor%20is%20flying%20away%2C%20but%20also%20not%20so%20heavy%20that%20each%20stroke%20is%20a%20chore.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EOn%20the%20other%20hand%2C%20the%20mouse's%20simplicity%20means%20that%20it%20lacks%20the%20ergonomic%20comfort%20of%20other%20options.%20Its%20symmetrical%20design%20doesn't%20account%20for%20the%20lopsided%20shape%20that%20a%20hand%20rests%20in%20while%20using%20a%20mouse.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20G305%20is%20also%20very%20small%20compared%20to%20other%20options%2C%20meaning%20users%20with%20larger%20hands%20or%20longer%20fingers%20may%20find%20it%20uncomfortable%20to%20use%20for%20long%20stints.%20After%20using%20mine%20for%20two%20years%2C%20I%20haven't%20found%20this%20to%20be%20a%20problem%2C%20but%20users%20with%20easily%20fatigued%20hands%20may%20want%20to%20consider%20something%20else.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-label%3D%5C%22Buttons%5C%22%3E%3Cstrong%3E6%20programmable%20buttons%20that%20do%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3Cstrong%3En't%20get%20in%20the%20way%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3E%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cfigure%3E%3Cstrong%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%222048%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22A%20hand%20holding%20the%20Logitech%20G305%20lightspeed%20mouse%20displaying%20the%20additional%20customizable%20buttons.%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F64e6b8df4a32f3001974a394%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%221536%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EThe%20thumb%20buttons%20are%20easy%20to%20reach%2C%20but%20not%20in%20the%20way.%3Cp%3ESarah%20Saril%2FInsider%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3EIn%20total%2C%20the%20Logitech%20G305%20h