src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F64e6b835912f290019aa304c%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%221536%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EThe%20DPI%20switcher%20is%20placed%20conveniently%20below%20the%20scroll%20wheel%20so%20you%20can%20adjust%20your%20sensitivity%20mid-game.%3Cp%3ESarah%20Saril%2FInsider%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3EThis%20mouse%20uses%20a%20small%2C%20low-profile%20USB-A%20dongle%20to%20connect%20to%20your%20laptop%20or%20computer.%20Setup%20is%20a%20breeze%20and%20connectivity%20is%20strong%2C%20even%20with%20objects%20obstructing%20the%20line%20of%20sight%20between%20mouse%20and%20dongle.%20I've%20never%20experienced%20disconnection%20issues%2C%20even%20when%20plugging%20it%20into%20a%20USB%20hub.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EJust%20like%20every%20other%20gaming%20mouse%20worth%20its%20salt%2C%20you%20can%20adjust%20the%20Logitech%20G305's%20DPI%20(dots%20per%20inch)%2C%20or%20its%20sensitivity%2C%20anywhere%20from%20200%20to%2012%2C000.%20The%20small%20button%20underneath%20the%20scroll%20wheel%20is%20actually%20a%20DPI%20switcher%20designed%20to%20quickly%20toggle%20its%20sensitivity%20by%20cycling%20through%20a%20range%20of%20common%20settings%3B%20you%20can%20also%20program%20the%20exact%20DPI%20numbers%20these%20correlate%20to%20in%20Logitech's%20software.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-label%3D%5C%22Battery%20life%5C%22%3E%3Cstrong%3ENot%20rechargeable%2C%20but%20battery%20life%20seriously%20lasts%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3E%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cfigure%3E%3Cstrong%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%222048%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22The%20logitech%20g305%20lightspeed%20with%20the%20cover%20removed%2C%20displaying%20the%20AA%20battery%20and%20USB%20dongle.%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F64e6b7d6912f290019aa3042%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%221536%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EIt%20connects%20wirelessly%20using%20a%20low-profile%20dongle%20that%20can%20be%20stored%2