%2C%20and%20has%20rallied%20more%20than%2056%25%20in%202023.%3C%2Fli%3E%5Cn%3C%2Ful%3E%3Cp%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fmarkets.businessinsider.com%2Fcurrencies%2Fbtc-usd%3Futm_medium%3Dingest%26utm_source%3Dmarkets%26utm_medium%3Dingest%26utm_source%3Dmarkets%5C%22%3EBitcoin%3C%2Fa%3E%20could%20surge%20to%20almost%20five%20times%20its%20current%20price%20by%202025%20after%20its%20halving%20cycle%20commences%20next%20year%2C%20according%20to%20research%20group%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fpanteracapital.com%2Fblockchain-letter%2Fa-positive-black-swan%2F%23_ftn1%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EPantera%20Capital%3C%2Fa%3E.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EIn%20a%20Tuesday%20note%2C%20analysts%20at%20the%20firm%20maintained%20their%20bullish%20outlook%20for%20the%20world's%20largest%20crypto%20by%20market%20cap%2C%20and%20said%20historical%20trends%20suggest%20plenty%20of%20upside%20ahead.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BBitcoin%20has%20historically%20bottomed%20477%20days%20prior%20to%20the%20halving%2C%20climbed%20leading%20into%20it%2C%20and%20then%20exploded%20to%20the%20upside%20afterwards%2C%26quot%3B%20Pantera%20Capital%20wrote.%20%26quot%3BThe%20post-halving%20rallies%20have%20averaged%20480%20days%20%E2%80%93%20from%20the%20halving%20to%20the%20peak%20of%20that%20next%20bull%20cycle.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EBy%20those%20measures%2C%20the%20strategists%20said%20bitcoin%20should%20have%20bottomed%20already%2C%20back%20in%20December%202022.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EHalving%2C%20which%20happens%20every%20four%20years%20for%20bitcoin%2C%20is%20when%20crypto%20miners'%20reward%20is%20cut%20in%20half%20to%20create%20a%20scarcity%20effect%2C%20according%20to%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fmarkets.businessinsider.com%2Fnews%2Fcurrencies%2Fwho-is-satoshi-nakamoto-bitcoin-inventor-crypto-steve-jobs-apple-2023-4%3Futm_medium%3Dingest%26utm_source%3Dmarkets%5C%22%3Ethe%20original%20whitepaper%20by%20Satoshi%20Nakamoto%3C%2Fa%3E.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EIn%2