kers%20of%20any%20age%20last%20year%2C%20according%20to%20LinkedIn's%20workforce%20report%20%E2%80%94%20up%20there%20with%20Austin%2C%20Texas%2C%20and%20San%20Francisco.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ESeveral%2020-somethings%20told%20Insider%20they%20chose%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fconfessions-genz-millennials-who-moved-to-tampa-florida-2023-7%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3E%3Cu%3ETampa%3C%2Fu%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%20for%20its%20relative%20affordability%2C%20and%20small-town%20feel.%20Compared%20with%20many%20bigger%20cities%2C%20renting%20or%20owning%20a%20home%20can%20be%20cheaper.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EBut%20the%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Faffiliate.insider.com%3Fh%3D8370f576f163a3b30f13bdf710decf45cb238710a2f6cf6fff3b5615ddf1327d%26postID%3D64e667d53b1480ff6c09f77d%26postSlug%3Dtampa-florida-plan-for-affordable-housing-2023-8%26site%3Dbi%26u%3Dhttps%253A%252F%252Fwww.linkedin.com%252Fposts%252Fkelsey-neubauer-34ba03a5_tampa-is-becoming-a-gen-z-hotspot-5-recent-activity-7090408080869371904-ivV6%253Futm_source%253Dshare%2526utm_medium%253Dmember_desktop%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3E%3Cu%3Einflux%20of%20new%20residents%3C%2Fu%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%20is%20part%20of%20what's%20prompting%20concerns%20about%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fmarkets.businessinsider.com%2Fnews%2Fcommodities%2Fflorida-housing-market-affordability-rent-home-prices-cost-of-living-2023-7%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Eaffordability%3C%2Fa%3E.%20Those%20worries%20are%20pushing%20the%20city%20to%20look%20for%20ways%20to%20get%20developers%20to%20build%20more%20housing%20%E2%80%94%C2%A0including%20affordable%20units%2C%20Tampa%20Mayor%20Jane%20Castor%20told%20Insider.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EA%20quick%20scan%20of%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fus-cities-metro-areas-most-exclusionary-housing-zoning-policies-2023-3%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Ethe%20Tampa%20market%3C%2Fa%3E%20reveals%20the%20scope%20of%20the%20challenge%3A%20The%20typical%20home%20price%20in%20Tampa%20in%20July%20was%20%24430%2C000%2C%20according%20to%20Redfin%20data%2C%20up%2068%25%20from%20the%20beginning%20of%202020.%20%3Cspan%3EOverall%2C%20%3C%2Fspan%3Ethe%20cost%20of%20a%20typical%3Cspan%3E%20US%20home%20went%20up%2045%25%20over%20the%20same%20period%2C%20per%20Redfin%20figures.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20average%20cost%20to%20rent%20a%20one-bedroom%20apartment%20in%20the%20city%20is%20%241%2C662%20per%20month%2C%20up%206%25%20since%20last%20year%2C%20according%20to%20Rent.com.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%222000%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22clearwater%20beach%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F64cbda000b651c00193a0805%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%221500%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EClearwater%20Beach%20near%20Tampa.%20%3Cp%3EIxefra%2FGetty%20Images%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3ECastor%20said%20that%20with%20so%20many%20new%20residents%20moving%20in%20and%20buying%20up%20property%2C%20it's%20been%20hard%20for%20some%20middle-income%20homeowners%20looking%20to%20size%20up%20to%20find%20a%20place%20to%20move%20to%20%E2%80%94%C2%A0because%20there%20is%20such%20limited%20supply.%20Meanwhile%2C%20some%20of%20Tampa's%20renters%20are%20overwhelmed%20by%20the%20price%20hikes%20as%20a%20result%20of%20the%20new%20demand%2C%20she%20added.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BFor%20residents%20of%20Tampa%2C%20it%20really%20has%20been%20a%20strange%20kind%20of%20burden%2C%26quot%3B%20Castor%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EIn%20order%20to%20ease%20the%20hardships%20that%20some%20residents%20are%20facing%2C%20Castor%20said%20the%20city%20is%20incentivizing%20developers%20to%20increase%20housing%20supply%20generally.%20This%20includes%20affordable-housing%20development.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EOne%20incentive%20Castor%20pointed%20to%20in%20a%202021%20press%20conference%20allowed%20a%20local%20developer%20to%20add%2031%20apartments%20to%20a%20proposal%20for%20a%20199-unit%20project.%20To%20get