0really%20taken%20to%20heart%2C%26quot%3B%20she%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ETo%20avoid%20this%2C%20Castor%20said%20she's%20eyeing%20land%20along%20transit%20routes%20to%20add%20to%20the%20land%20trust.%20That%20could%20make%20it%20so%20that%20those%20living%20in%20housing%20that%20gets%20built%20nearby%20won't%20necessarily%20have%20to%20rely%20on%20a%20car%20to%20get%20around.%20The%20aim%20is%20to%20help%20maintain%20economic%20and%20racial%20diversity%20throughout%20Tampa's%20neighborhoods%2C%20she%20said%2C%20and%20avoid%20displacement%20in%20neighborhoods%20that%20see%20an%20influx%20of%20wealthier%20residents.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BOur%20identity%20is%20rooted%20in%20diversity%2C%26quot%3B%20Castor%20said.%20%26quot%3BWe%20want%20people%20to%20live%20in%20the%20neighborhood%20they%20want%20to%20live%20in.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cdiv%3ERead%20the%20original%20article%20on%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Ftampa-florida-plan-for-affordable-housing-2023-8%5C%22%3EBusiness%20Insider%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1692903512000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F64c162ef9440b70019267348%3Fformat%3Djpeg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Ftampa-florida-plan-for-affordable-housing-2023-8%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Here%20is%20how%20Tampa%2C%20Florida%2C%20will%20build%20more%20affordable%20housing%20for%20residents%20as%20the%20population%20increases.%20Tampa%20is%20becoming%20a%20hot%20spot%20for%20movers.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22kneubauer%40insider.com%20(Kelsey%20Neubauer)%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A4%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Ftampa-florida-plan-for-affordable-housing-2023-8%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Springsteen%20Covers%20Springsteen%3A%20Check%20Out%20Alana%E2%80%99s%20Version%20of%20Bruce%E2%80%99s%20%E2%80%98I%E2%80%99m%20on%20Fire%E2%80%99%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%22%2C%22published%22%3A16929