C%26quot%3B%20he%20added%2C%20in%20what%20appeared%20to%20be%20a%20reference%20to%20Putin.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EA%20'common%20cause'%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EMoscow%20had%20initially%20said%20only%20that%20the%2062-year-old%20Prigozhin%20was%20listed%20as%20a%20passenger%20on%20the%20flight%2C%20without%20confirming%20his%20death.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EBut%20when%20Putin%20broke%20his%20silence%20on%20Thursday%20he%20paid%20a%20qualified%20tribute%20to%20the%20mercenary%20boss%20and%20the%20paramilitary%20group%20he%20led.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BI%20knew%20Prigozhin%20for%20a%20very%20long%20time%2C%20since%20the%20early%2090s.%20He%20was%20a%20man%20of%20complicated%20fate%2C%20and%20he%20made%20serious%20mistakes%20in%20his%20life%2C%20but%20he%20achieved%20the%20right%20results%2C%26quot%3B%20Putin%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%20an%20address%20to%20Russians%20during%20the%20Wagner%20rebellion%20on%20June%2023-24%20in%20which%20he%20warned%20against%20%26quot%3Bcivil%20war%26quot%3B%2C%20Putin%20had%20called%20Prigozhin%20--%20once%20his%20ally%20--%20a%20%26quot%3Btraitor%26quot%3B.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EBut%20on%20Thursday%2C%20he%20said%20the%20Wagner%20members%20who%20had%20died%20in%20the%20crash%20had%20made%20a%20%26quot%3Bsignificant%20contribution%26quot%3B%20to%20Moscow's%20offensive%20in%20Ukraine.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThey%20had%20shared%20a%20common%20cause%2C%20Putin%20said%2C%20adding%3A%20%26quot%3BWe%20remember%20that%2C%20we%20know%20that%2C%20and%20we%20will%20not%20forget%20that.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3E'Reasonable%20doubts'%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ESome%20Western%20leaders%20expressed%20doubts%20that%20the%20crash%20had%20been%20an%20accident.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThere's%20not%20much%20that%20happens%20in%20Russia%20that%20Putin's%20not%20behind%2C%26quot%3B%20said%20US%20President%20Joe%20Biden%2C%20after%20having%20said%20he%20did%20not%20know%20what%20happened.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EFrance%20saw%20%26quot%3Breasonable%20doubts%26quot%3B%20about%20the%20crash%2C%20while%20Germany%20said%20it%20followed%20a%20pattern%20of%20%26quot%3Bunclarified%26quot%3B%20fatalities%20in%20Russia.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EGerman%20Foreign%20Minister%20Annalena%20Baerbock%20appeared%20to%20say%20it%20was%20suspicious%20that%20%26quot%3Ba%20disgraced%20former%20confidant%20of%20Putin%20suddenly%2C%20literally%20falls%20from%20the%20sky%20two%20months%20after%20he%20attempted%20a%20mutiny%26quot%3B.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EEven%20influential%20pro-Kremlin%20figures%2C%20such%20as%20state%20television%20personality%20and%20Putin%20ally%20Margarita%20Simonyan%2C%20seemed%20to%20suggest%20that%20it%20could%20have%20been%20an%20assassination.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BAmong%20the%20versions%20that%20are%20being%20discussed%20(about%20the%20crash)%20is%20that%20it%20was%20staged.%20But%20personally%2C%20I'm%20leaning%20towards%20the%20more%20obvious%20one%2C%26quot%3B%20she%20said%20on%20social%20media.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ERussia's%20aviation%20authority%20published%20the%20names%20of%20those%20on%20board%20the%20Embraer%20private%20jet%20late%20on%20Wednesday.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIt%20included%20Prigozhin%20and%20his%20right-hand%20man%2C%20Dmitry%20Utkin%2C%20a%20shadowy%20figure%20who%20managed%20Wagner's%20operations%20and%20allegedly%20served%20in%20Russian%20military%20intelligence.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ERussian%20police%20patrolled%20the%20crash%20site%20near%20the%20village%20of%20Kuzhenkino%2C%20some%20350%20kilometres%20(220%20miles)%20north%20of%20Moscow%20in%20the%20Tver%20region.%20Some%20masked%20men%20carried%20rifles.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EOne%20woman%20living%20near%20Kuzhenkino%20said%20her%20neighbour%20had%20heard%20a%20roar%20and%20saw%20%26quot%3Bsparkling%20from%20the%20plane%26quot%3B%2C%20accompanied%20by%20fire.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BA%20neighbour%20ran%20up%20to%20me%20with%20shaking%20hands%20and%20when%20we%20went%20to%20the%20window%20I%20saw%20only%20one%20mushroom%20(a%20cloud%20from%20the%20explosion)%2C%20a%20black%20cloud%2C%26quot%3B%20she%20said%20in%20video%20published%20by%20state-run%20news%20agency%20RIA%20Novosti.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3E'Real%20patriot'%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EVideo%20verified%20by%20AFP%20from%20the%20scene%20appeared%20to%20show%20the%20Embraer%20Legacy%20plane%20engulfed%20in%20a%20plume-like%20column%20of%20white%20smoke%20as%20it%20fell%20from%20the%20sky.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20Flightradar24%20tracker%20website%20said%20the%20plane%20flying%20from%20Moscow%20to%20Saint%20Peterburg%20appeared%20on%20their%20radar%20until%20the%20last%2030%20seconds%20and%20descended%20%26quot%3Bdramatically%26quot%3B%20at%20around%2015%3A20%20GMT.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ESome%20Wagner-linked%20Telegram%20channels%20initially%20suggested%20the%20plane%20had%20been%20shot%20down%20by%20Russian%20air%20defence%2C%20on%20a%20day%20when%20Kyiv%20struck%20Russia%20with%20more%20drone%20attacks.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EPrigozhin%20appeared%20to%20enjoy%20some%20popularity%20in%20Russia.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHe%20appealed%20to%20nationalist-leaning%20Russians%20--%20also%20suspicious%20of%20the%20army%20leadership%20during%20the%20Ukraine%20offensive%20--%20who%20embraced%20his%20tough-guy%20style.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ESome%20even%20speculated%20that%20he%20would%20take%20part%20in%20the%202024%20presidential%20election%2C%20which%20is%20expected%20to%20extend%20Putin's%20rule%20until%20at%20least%202030.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BHe%20was%20one%20of%20the%20few%20real%20patriots%20in%20our%20country%2C%26quot%3B%20Pavel%20Zakharov%20said%20as%20he%20laid%20flowers%20at%20Wagner's%20headquarters%20in%20Saint%20Petersburg.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EMany%20Russians%20eagerly%20awaited%20Prigozhin's%20outspoken%2C%20often%20expletive-laden%20social%20media%20videos%2C%20a%20sharp%20contrast%20to%20the%20tightly%20controlled%20narrative%20of%20Russian%20officials.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%