3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EThe%20guidelines%20said%20doctors%20should%20prescribe%20generic%20medicines%2C%20and%20that%20medical%20conferences%20should%20not%20be%20organised%20through%20the%20sponsorship%20of%20pharma%20companies.%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EThe%20guidelines%20also%20said%20that%20doctors%20should%20not%20endorse%20any%20product%20and%20should%20try%20to%20digitise%20medical%20records%20of%20patients%2C%20among%20other%20things.%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EThe%20issue%20of%20generic%20medicines%20had%20sparked%20debates%2C%20but%20now%20the%20government%20has%20decided%20to%20put%20the%20entire%20set%20of%20regulations%20on%20hold%20after%20a%20representation%20by%20the%20Indian%20Medical%20Association%20(IMA).%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EThe%20August%2023%20notification%20put%20these%20guidelines%20in%20abeyance%20with%20immediate%20effect.%C2%A0%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EIt%20said%20that%20the%20professional%20rules%20and%20regulations%20would%20be%20guided%20by%20a%20set%20of%20guidelines%20which%20were%20framed%20in%202002%20and%20superseded%20by%20the%20new%20rules.%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EIn%20essence%2C%20the%20ethics%20and%20regulations%20for%20doctors%20have%20been%20reversed%20to%20those%20framed%20about%2021%20years%20ago.%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3E%3Cins%3EAlso%20read%3A%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fhealth%2Fdoctors-organisations-find-novel-ways-to-organise-conferences-without-pharma-backing%5C%22%3ENMC%20Guidelines%3A%20Doctors%E2%80%99%20Orgs%20Find%20%E2%80%98Novel%E2%80%99%20Ways%20to%20Organise%20Conferences%20Without%20Pharma%20Backing%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fins%3E%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EThe%202002%20guidelines%20also%20had%20some%20of%20these%20provisions%2C%20like%20doctors%20not%20being%20allowed%20to%20travel%20on%20tickets%20sponsored%20by%20pharma%20companies%2C%20endorsement%20of%20medical%20products%2C%20etc.%C2%A0%20But%20these%20did%20not%20have%20specific%20provisions%20of%20legal%20penalties%20which%20the%20new%20set%20of%20regulations%20had.%20The%202002%20code%20of%20conduct%20said%20if%20any%20of%20the%20professional%20rules%20mentioned%20in%20it%20were%20violated%2C%20the%20state%20medical%20councils%20may%20take%20action%20%E2%80%9Cas%20deemed%20necessary%E2%80%9D%20or%20may%20direct%20the%20removal%20altogether%20or%20for%20a%20specified%20period%2C%20from%20the%20register%20of%20the%20name%20of%20the%20delinquent%20registered%20practitioner.%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EOn%20the%20other%20hand%2C%20the%20new%20rules%20were%20not%20more%20specific%20in%20terms%20of%20what%20they%20mandated%20but%20also%20in%20terms%20of%20punishments%2C%20and%20as%20such%2C%20it%20proposed%20three%20levels%20of%20punishments%20%E2%80%94%20from%20issuance%20of%20advisory%20to%20suspension%20of%20licence%20for%20one%20month%20to%20three%20months.%20And%20for%20each%20violation%2C%20the%20rules%20had%20specified%20which%20level%20of%20punishment%20would%20be%20awarded.%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EThe%20IMA%20had%20raised%20huge%20hue%20and%20cry%20against%20the%20new%20rules%20and%20its%20delegation%20met%20Union%20health%20minister%20Mansukh%20Mandaviya%20on%20August%2021.%20The%20IMA%20has%20termed%20the%20NMC%20rescinding%20on%20the%20new%20guidelines%20as%20a%20%E2%80%9Cgrand%20victory%E2%80%9D%20and%20thanked%20Mandaviya%20for%20heeding%20to%20its%20demands.%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1692892859000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F08%2F24212848%2Fimage-1244.png%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fgovernment%2Fnmc-puts-new-guidelines-on-doctors-ethics-in-abeyance-after-imas-meeting-with-health-minister%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22The%20new%20notification%20of%20NMC%20says%20the%20conduct%20of%20the%20doctors%20would%20continue%20to%20be%20guided%20by%20the%20rules%20that%20were%20established%2021%20years%20ago.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fgovernment%2Fnmc-puts-new-guidelines-on-doctors-ethics-in-abeyance-after-imas-meeting-with-health-minister%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22What%20now%20for%20Wagner%20after%20Prigozhin's%20reported%20death%3F%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%22%2C%22published%22%3A1692892813000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fichef.bbci.co.uk%2Fnews%2F1024%2Fbranded_news%2F3D67%2Fproduction%2F_130891751_prigozhin.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.bbc.co.uk%2Fnews%2Fworld-europe-66604261%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22With%20a%20global%20military%20footprint%2C%20experts%20are%20asking%20how%20Wagner%20will%20fill%20the%20void%20left%20by%20its%20leader.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A75%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.bbc.co.uk%2Fnews%2Fworld-europe-66604261%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww-bbc-co-uk.cdn.ampproject.org%2Fc%2Fs%2Fwww.bbc.co.uk%2Fnews%2Fworld-europe-66604261.amp%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.bbc.co.uk%2Fnews%2Fworld-europe-66604261.amp%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Vivek%20Ramaswamy%20hogs%20airtime%20and%20smackdowns%20in%20first%20GOP%20debate%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%22%2C%22published%22%3A1692892373000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.toiimg.com%2Fphoto%2Fmsid-103032297%2Cimgsize-1532764.cms%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Ftimesofindia.indiatimes.com%2Fworld%2Fus%2Fvivek-ramaswamy-hogs-airtime-and-smackdowns-in-first-gop-debate%2Farticleshow%2F103031687.cms%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Vivek%20Ramaswamy%2C%20an%20Indian-American%20entrepreneur%2C%20made%20an%20impact%20during%20the%20Republican%20Presidential%20debate%20by%20positioning%20himself%20as%20an%20anti-establishment%20outsider%20and%20aligning%20with%20Donald%20Trump's%20vision.%20