%20areas%20along%20the%20India-China%20border%2C%26quot%3B%20Foreign%20Secretary%20Vinay%20Kwatra%20told%20reporters%20today.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EMr%20Kwatra%20said%20PM%20Modi%20underlined%20that%20the%20maintenance%20of%20peace%20and%20tranquility%20in%20border%20areas%2C%20and%20respecting%20the%20LAC%20are%20essential%20for%20the%20normalisation%20of%20India-China%20relationship.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BIn%20this%20regard%2C%20the%20two%20leaders%20agreed%20to%20direct%20their%20relevant%20officials%20to%20intensify%20efforts%20at%20expeditious%20disengagement%20and%20de-escalation%2C%26quot%3B%20the%20Foreign%20Secretary%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%2019th%20round%20of%20India-China%20Corps%20Commander-level%20meeting%20was%20held%20at%20the%20Chushul-Moldo%20border%20meeting%20point%20on%20the%20Indian%20side%20on%20August%2013-14.%20The%20two%20sides%20had%20a%20positive%2C%20constructive%20and%20in-depth%20discussion%20on%20the%20resolution%20of%20the%20remaining%20issues%20along%20the%20LAC%20in%20the%20western%20sector%2C%20the%20Foreign%20Ministry%20had%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%20line%20with%20the%20guidance%20provided%20by%20the%20leadership%2C%20they%20exchanged%20views%20in%20an%20open%20and%20forward-looking%20manner%2C%20the%20ministry%20had%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20BRICS%20Summit%20was%20chaired%20by%20South%20African%20President%20Cyril%20Ramaphosa.%20Brazil's%20President%20Luiz%20Inacio%20Lula%20da%20Silva%20also%20attended%2C%20while%20Russian%20President%20Vladimir%20Putin%20joined%20it%20through%20video%20conference.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EA%20declaration%20unveiled%20at%20the%20end%20of%20the%20three-day%20BRICS%20(Brazil%2C%20Russia%2C%20India%2C%20China%2C%20South%20Africa)%20Summit%20said%20the%20leaders%20of%20the%20grouping%20called%20for%20an%20expeditious%20finalisation%20and%20adoption%20of%20the%20Comprehensive%20Convention%20on%20International%20Terrorism%20within%20the%20UN%20framework.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26qu