0that%20might%20make%20him%20proud.%20%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BIt's%20little%20bit%20funny%20that%20I%20faced%20almost%20zero%20players%20in%20their%20prime.%20I%20played%20Chuky%20(Vasyl%20Ivanchuk)%20and%20then%20I%20played%20three%20youngsters.%20So%2C%20yeah%2C%20obviously%20they%20are%20very%2C%20very%20strong.%20I%20felt%20like%20I%20had%20my%20by%20far%20best%20day%20and%20game%20of%20the%20event%20against%20Gukesh%20on%20the%20first%20day.%20Otherwise%2C%20that%20match%20would've%20been%20extremely%20tough.%20As%20for%20the%20others%2C%20they%20are%20very%20strong.%20Vincent%20(Keymer)%20pushed%20me%20the%20hardest%2C%20he%20was%20one%20move%20away%20from%20eliminating%20me%2C%20and%20leaving%20everything%20else%20moot%2C%26quot%3B%20Carlsen%20said%20on%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.youtube.com%2Fwatch%3Fv%3D5SAw3OIrNk0%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EChess%2024%3C%2Fa%3E%20after%20winning%20his%20maiden%20Chess%20World%20Cup%20title.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThey%20are%20all%20very%20good%2C%20Gukesh%20is%20clearly%20the%20strongest%20classical%20player%20right%20now.%20And%20then%2C%20you%20have%20Pragg%20and%20(Nodirbek)%20Abdusattorov%20who%20are%20really%20strong%20but%20also%20mentality%20monsters.%20And%20then%2C%20I%20think%20on%20a%20tier%20slightly%20below%2C%20we%20have%20Vincent%20and%20a%20few%20others.%20But%20what%20I%20think%20is%20pretty%20clear%20is%20that%20chess%20is%20in%20good%20hands%20for%20the%20future.%20The%20generation%20of%20players%2C%20born%20from%201990-1994%20really%20have%20dominated%20for%20a%20long%20time%2C%20and%20finally%20now%2C%20with%20these%20youngsters%20born%20in%202003%20and%20after%2C%20we%20have%20a%20generation%20that's%20worthy%20of%20succeeding%20us.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThough%2C%20Praggnanandhaa%20had%20to%20settle%20for%20the%20position%20of%20runner-up%20of%20the%202023%20FIDE%20World%20Cup%20but%20he%20will%20draw%20hope%20from%20the%20fact%20that%20he%20has%20qualfied%20for%20the%20FIDE%20Candidates%20tournament.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%202024%20Candidates%20Tournament%20will%20be%20an%20eight-player%20chess%20tournament%20scheduled%20to%20be%20held%20from%202%20April%20to%2025%20April%202024%20in%20Toronto%2C%20Canada.%20The%20winner%20of%20the%20tournament%20will%20becomne%20the%20challenger%20for%20the%202024%20World%20Chess%20Championship%20match.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EPraggnanandhaa%20had%20an%20excellent%20tournament%20where%20he%20defeated%20World%20No.%202%20Hikaru%20Nakamura%20in%20a%20tie-breaker%20while%20reaching%20the%20final%20defeating%20World%20No.%203%20Fabiano%20Caruana.%20%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EWith%20ANI%20inputs%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1692891480000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2023-08%2Fmtg5qon8_carlsen-vs-praggnanandhaa_625x300_23_August_23.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fsports.ndtv.com%2Fchess%2Fmentality-monster-r-praggnanandhaa-gets-viral-worthy-tag-from-magnus-carlsen-after-terrific-chess-world-cup-final-4326773%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22India's%20R%20Praggnanandhaa%2C%20over%20the%20last%20three%20days%20at%20the%20Chess%20World%20Cup%20final%20against%20Magnus%20Carlsen%2C%20showed%20the%20world%20that%20he%20is%20here%20to%20stay%20at%20the%20top%20in%20chess%20for%20years%20to%20come.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A4%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fsports.ndtv.com%2Fchess%2Fmentality-monster-r-praggnanandhaa-gets-viral-worthy-tag-from-magnus-carlsen-after-terrific-chess-world-cup-final-4326773%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fsports-ndtv-com.cdn.ampproject.org%2Fc%2Fs%2Fsports.ndtv.com%2Fchess%2Fmentality-monster-r-praggnanandhaa-gets-viral-worthy-tag-from-magnus-carlsen-after-terrific-chess-world-cup-final-4326773%2Famp%2F1%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fsports.ndtv.com%2Fchess%2Fmentality-monster-r-praggnanandhaa-gets-viral-worthy-tag-from-magnus-carlsen-after-terrific-chess-world-cup-final-4326773%2Famp%