0football's%20governing%20body%20said%20in%20a%20statement.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EFIFA%20said%20the%20incident%20%26quot%3Bmay%20constitute%20violations%20of%20article%2013%20paragraphs%201%20and%202%20of%20the%20FIFA%20disciplinary%20code%26quot%3B.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ESpain%20star%20Hermoso%20released%20a%20joint%20statement%20with%20union%20Futpro%20on%20Wednesday%2C%20which%20called%20for%20action%20to%20be%20taken%20against%20the%20RFEF%20president.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BWe%20are%20working%20to%20ensure%20that%20acts%20such%20as%20those%20we%20have%20seen%20never%20go%20unpunished%2C%20that%20they%20are%20sanctioned%20and%20that%20the%20exemplary%20measures%20are%20adopted%20to%20protect%20women%20footballers%20from%20actions%20that%20we%20believe%20are%20unacceptable%2C%26quot%3B%20the%20statement%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHuman%20rights%20organisation%20Amnesty%20International%20offered%20their%20backing%20to%20Hermoso%20on%20Thursday.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BAmnesty%20International%20wants%20to%20show%20their%20support%20for%20the%20demands%20of%20the%20player%2C%20who%20has%20asked%20the%20(RFEF)%20to%20set%20underway%20'exemplary%20measures'%20regarding%20the%20non-consensual%20kiss%2C%26quot%3B%20said%20the%20organisation%20in%20a%20statement.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3B(We)%20underline%20that%20this%20behaviour%20is%20a%20form%20of%20sexual%20violence%20like%20any%20other%2C%20and%20cannot%20be%20justified%20in%20any%20way.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ESpain's%20women's%20football%20league%2C%20Liga%20F%2C%20has%20also%20called%20for%20Rubiales%20to%20be%20sacked.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20RFEF%20have%20opened%20an%20investigation%20into%20Rubiales'%20conduct%20and%20are%20holding%20an%20emergency%20meeting%20on%20Friday.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ERubiales%2C%2046%2C%20initially%20attacked%20his%20critics%20before%20eventually%20apologising%20but%20the%20criticism%20of%20his%20behaviour%20has%20not%20abated.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ESpanish%20prim