cial%20media%20handles%20of%20the%20news%20outlet.%20They%20also%20condemned%20the%20blocking%20of%20access%20to%20the%20social%20media%20handles%20of%20%3Cem%3EGaon%20Savera%3C%2Fem%3E%2C%20a%20news%20outlet.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CThe%20Press%20Club%20of%20India%20and%20the%20undersigned%20media%20bodies%20as%20institutions%20dedicated%20to%20upholding%20the%20principles%20of%20free%20speech%2C%20independent%20journalism%2C%20and%20the%20democratic%20values%20of%20our%20country%2C%20find%20the%20blocking%20of%20%3Cem%3EKashmir%20Walla%3C%2Fem%3E%E2%80%98s%20digital%20platforms%20unilaterally%20without%20citing%20any%20reason%20deeply%20alarming.%20The%20act%20of%20blocking%20access%20without%20any%20prior%20notice%2C%20official%20communication%2C%20or%20an%20opportunity%20for%20the%20concerned%20party%20to%20address%20any%20grievances%20is%20a%20clear%20violation%20of%20the%20fundamental%20rights%20enshrined%20in%20our%20Constitution%2C%E2%80%9D%20the%20statement%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20media%20bodies%20also%20said%20the%20arrest%20of%20the%20editor%20of%20%3Cem%3EKashmir%20Walla%3C%2Fem%3E%20%E2%80%9Cwithout%20transparent%20justification%E2%80%9D%20sends%20a%20%E2%80%9Cchilling%20message%E2%80%9D%20to%20journalists%20across%20the%20country.%20They%20appealed%20to%20the%20government%20to%20allow%20media%20professionals%20to%20carry%20out%20their%20work%20without%20fear%20of%20retribution%20or%20intimidation.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20action%20against%20the%20Kashmir%20news%20outlet%20comes%20at%20a%20time%20when%20its%20editor%C2%A0%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22http%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Ftag%2Ffahad-shah%2F%5C%22%3EFahad%20Shah%3C%2Fa%3E%20has%20remained%20incarcerated%20in%20a%20Jammu%20jail%20for%2018%20months%20on%20terrorism%20charges%2C%20while%20Sajad%20Gul%2C%20a%20trainee%20reporter%20with%20the%20outlet%2C%20is%20also%20languishing%20in%20a%20prison%20in%20Uttar%20Pradesh%20from%20January%202022%20under%20the%20Public%20Safety%20Act.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3C