security%2Frailway-protection-force-constable-shoots-dead-asi-three-others-in-train%5C%22%3ERailway%20Protection%20Force%20(RPF)%20constable%20Chetan%20Singh%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20more%20so%20because%20we%20do%20not%20have%20a%20way%20to%20understand%20it%20in%20the%20India%20that%20was%20%E2%80%93%20the%20one%20that%20promised%20itself%20that%20it%20would%20be%20one%20created%20by%20%E2%80%9CWe%2C%20the%20people%20of%20India%E2%80%9D.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EFor%20too%20many%2C%20especially%20in%20the%20wake%20of%20the%20violence%20against%20the%20Muslims%20of%20Nuh%2C%20and%20the%20perpetual%20stoking%20of%20violence%20and%20hate%20against%20Muslims%20over%20the%20last%20decade%2C%20it%20is%20a%20story%20of%20the%20fear%20of%20minorities%20in%20a%20state%20that%20will%20not%20keep%20them%20safe.%20This%20is%20a%20superficial%20reading%2C%20and%20one%20that%20mistakes%20the%20gravity%20of%20the%20crime.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EMuslims%20have%20never%20felt%20safe%20in%20India%2C%20but%20then%20that%20is%20also%20true%20of%20most%20minorities%20anywhere%20in%20the%20country.%20Ask%20any%20Sikh%20family.%20The%20memories%20and%20stories%20of%20what%20happened%20to%20them%20or%20their%20loved%20ones%20during%20the%20violence%20of%20the%2080s%20%E2%80%93%20not%20just%20the%20cataclysmic%20killings%20after%20the%20assassination%20of%20Indira%20Gandhi%20%E2%80%93%20are%20not%20that%20far%20away.%20Ask%20Dalit%20families%20who%20have%20seen%20their%20community%20members%20murdered%2C%20tortured%2C%20raped%2C%20or%20socially%20sanctioned%2C%20and%20how%20those%20crimes%20have%20been%20covered%20up%20or%20ritually%20ignored%2C%20and%20you%20will%20learn%20a%20new%20measure%20of%20shame.%20Talk%20to%20those%20we%20call%20%E2%80%98tribal%E2%80%99%20people%20who%20have%20been%2C%20and%20still%20are%20being%2C%20written%20away%20from%20the%20land%20that%20they%20have%20inhabited%20from%20time%20immemorial%2C%20and%20you%20question%20exactly%20who%20are%20%E2%80%9CWe%2C%20the%20people%20of%20India%E2%80%9D.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EIn%202005%2C%20I%20recall%20talking%20to%20a%20patriarch%20of%20a%20Kashmiri%20Hindu%20family%20in%20Mattan%2C%20in%20the%20district%20official%20maps%20label%20Anantnag%20and%20locals%20often%20refer%20to%20as%20Islamabad%2C%20who%20had%20just%20been%20elected%20in%20the%20J%26amp%3BK%20municipal%20elections.%20The%20state%20had%20bucked%20a%20trend%2C%20electing%20far%20more%20minorities%20than%20their%20actual%20percentage%2C%20a%20thing%20unheard%20of%20in%20India%2C%20or%20most%20first-past-the-post%20electoral%20democracies.%20His%20family%20were%20the%20four%20Hindu%20people%20in%20that%20municipality%20and%20yet%20he%20had%20won.%20He%20had%20been%20dismissive%20of%20the%20soldiers%20around%20the%20temple%20and%20the%20multiple%20abandoned%20houses%20in%20the%20neighbourhood.%20%E2%80%9CIt%20isn%E2%80%99t%20them%20that%20keep%20me%20safe%2C%20it%20is%20my%20neighbours%2C%20who%20elected%20me%2C%20that%20do%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20had%20said.%20I%20had%20wondered%20if%20his%20family%20made%20the%20same%20brave%20statement%2C%20but%20did%20not%20have%20the%20courage%20to%20ask.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EThe%20promise%20of%20safety%20for%20those%20in%20the%20numerical%20or%20political%20minority%20anywhere%20across%20India%20has%20been%20observed%20more%20in%20the%20breach%20than%20in%20the%20honouring%20of%20it.%20There%20has%20never%20been%20a%20guarantee%20of%20safety.%20We%20have%20lived%20with%20each%20other%2C%20loved%20each%20other%2C%20fought%20and%20reconciled%20with%20each%20other%2C%20kept%20our%20deep%20hurts%20and%20tried%20to%20keep%20going%2C%20despite%20all%20of%20that.%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EThe%20murder%20of%20people%20simply%20for%20the%20sake%20of%20their%20identity%2C%20however%20grotesque%2C%20is%20sadly%20%E2%80%93%20grievously%20%E2%80%93%20nothing%20new%20in%20a%20country%20with%20tens%20of%20millions%20of%20%E2%80%9C%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thehindu.com%2Fnews%2Fnational%2F46-million-girls-went-missing-in-india%2Farticle31957348.ece%5C%22%3Emissing%20women%3C%2Fa%3E%E2%80%9D%20%E2%80%93%20girl%20children%20never%20allowed%20to%20live%20simply%20because%20of%20their%20sex.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cins%3EAlso%20Read%3A%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fcommunalism%2Frpf-constable-who-killed-people-on-moving-train-has-a-history-of-assaulting-muslims-report%5C%22%3ERPF%20Constable%20Who%20Killed%20People%20on%20Moving%20Train%20Has%20a%20History%20of%20Assaulting%20Muslims%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fins%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EWhat%20makes%20Chetan%20Singh%E2%80%99s%20murders%20stand%20out%20is%20his%20invocation%20of%20Narendra%20Modi%20and%20Adityanath%20afterward.%20This%20is%20the%20crux%20of%20the%20matter.%20And%20if%20we%20turn%20to%20the%20US%20to%20learn%20about%20bigotry%20and%20lynchings%2C%20we%20must%20turn%20to%20China%20to%20learn%20of%20murders%20in%20the%20name%20of%20a%20paramount%20leader.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EIn%201966%2C%20and%20for%20a%20decade%20later%20%E2%80%93%20until%20his%20death%20%E2%80%93%20Mao%20rode%20on%20the%20storms%20of%20the%20Cultural%20Revolution%2C%20one%20of%20the%20single%20greatest%20self-destructive%20acts%20a%20country%20has%20committed%20in%20modern%20history.%20Feeling%20his%20control%20slip%20over%20the%20Communist%20Party%20of%20China%2C%20Mao%20turned%20to%20young%20men%20and%20women%20of%20the%20nation%2C%20suggesting%20that%20parts%20of%20the%20remaining%20%E2%80%98counter-revolutionary%20bourgeoise%20elite%E2%80%99%20were%20still%20in%20positions%20of%20power.%20Bands%20of%20young%20Chinese%20were%20allowed%20to%20form%20Red%20Guards%2C%20quoting%20Mao%E2%80%99s%20maxims%20from%20his%20Little%20Red%20Book%2C%20they%20were%20allowed%20free%20rein%20by%20the%20police%2C%20and%20could%20attack%20anybody.%20Schoolchildren%20accused%2C%20humiliated%20and%20attacked%20their%20teachers.%20Zhou%20Enlai%20had%20to%20warn%20members%20of%20the%20foreign%20service%20from%20stepping%20out%20for%20fear%20of%20being%20kidnapped%20or%20killed.%20In%20certain%20Chinese%20embassies%20around%20the%20world%2C%20the%20lower-ranking%20officers%20overthrew%20ambassadors%20and%20punished%20them%20for%20not%20being%20revolutionary%20enough.%20Tibetan%20monks%20were%20forced%20to%20destroy%20their%20own%20monasteries.%20Anything%20and%20everything%20was%20allowed%20in%20attacking%20the%20Four%20Olds%20%E2%80%93%20old%20customs%2C%20culture%2C%20ideas%2C%20and%20habits%2C%20all%20in%20the%20name%20of%20Mao.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3ENobody%20has%20an%20exact%20measure%20of%20how%20many%20died%20in%20the%20massacres%20of%20this%20time%2C%20though%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.sciencespo.fr%2Fmass-violence-war-massacre-resistance%2Fen%2Fdocument%2Fchronology-mass-killings-during-chinese-cultural-revolution-1966-1976.html%5C%22%3Eestimates%20range%3C%2Fa%3E%20from%20hundreds%20of%20thousands%20to%20millions.%20The%20cultural%20toll%20was%20extreme%2C%20so%20much%20so%20that%20one%20of%20the%20reasons%20that%20a%20character%20loses%20hope%20for%20humans%20in%20Liu%20Cixin%E2%80%99s%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.goodreads.com%2Fbook%2Fshow%2F20518872-the-three-body-problem%5C%22%3E%3Ci%3E%3Cspan%3EThe%20Three-Body%20Problem%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fi%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%3Cspan%3E%20%E2%80%93%20the%20most%20famous%20science%20fiction%20novel%20written%20by%20a%20Chinese%20person%20%E2%80%93%20is%20the%20Cultural%20Revolution.%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EAll%20of%20this%20was%20acceptable%20to%20Mao.%20He%20was%20the%20Supreme%20Leader.%20He%20was%20building%20a%20New%20China.%20He%20was%20above%20any%20constitution%20or%20law%2C%20and%20his%20followers%20%E2%80%93%20the%20Red%20Guards%20%E2%80%93%20were%20thus%20empowered.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%20class%3D%5C%22wp-caption%5C%22%