0were%20to%20make%20it%20to%20the%20winners%E2%80%99%20podium%2C%20the%20national%20anthem%20will%20not%20be%20played.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20WFI%E2%80%99s%20membership%20was%20suspended%20because%20of%20the%20lack%20of%20elections%20in%20the%20organisation.%20Elections%20were%20supposed%20to%20be%20held%20in%20June%202023%2C%20but%20they%20were%20postponed.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20WFI%20has%20been%20mired%20in%20controversy%20over%20the%20last%20year%2C%20with%20a%20number%20of%20medal-winning%20wrestlers%20accusing%20the%20federation%E2%80%99s%20president%20and%20Bharatiya%20Janata%20Party%20MP%20Brij%20Bhushan%20Sharan%20Singh%20of%20sexual%20assault%20and%20various%20forms%20of%20harassment.%20The%20wrestlers%20accused%20the%20Union%20government%20of%20protecting%20the%20BJP%20leader%2C%20and%20held%20a%20months-long%20protest%20in%20Delhi%20before%20being%20displaced%20by%20the%20police.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EUWW%20intimated%20the%20Indian%20Olympic%20Association%20of%20its%20decision%20in%20a%20letter%2C%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Findianexpress.com%2Farticle%2Fsports%2Fsport-others%2Fwfi-suspended-wrestlers-to-compete-under-neutral-flag-8907013%2F%5C%22%3E%3Cem%3EThe%20Indian%20Express%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%20reported.%20.%20%E2%80%9CThe%20IOA%20has%20received%20a%20communication%20and%20will%20decide%20the%20future%20course%20of%20action%2C%20including%20the%20selection%20of%20teams%20for%20the%20World%20Championships%2C%E2%80%9D%20an%20official%20told%20the%20newspaper.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%20June%2C%20when%20there%20had%20been%20widespread%20coverage%20of%20the%20wrestlers%E2%80%99%20protest%20and%20the%20police%E2%80%99s%20manhandling%20and%20detention%20of%20wrestlers%2C%20the%20UWW%20had%20threatened%20to%20suspend%20India%E2%80%99s%20membership%20to%20protest%20the%20treatment%20of%20athletes.%20At%20the%20time%2C%20it%20had%20given%20the%20WFI%20a%2045-day%20deadline%20to%20hold%20elections%2C%20and%20said%20%E2%80%9CFailing%20to%20do%20so