ky.com%2Fstory%2Fprigozhin-crash-military-analyst-sean-bell-on-what-the-footage-tells-us-12946365%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fnews-sky-com.cdn.ampproject.org%2Fc%2Fs%2Fnews.sky.com%2Fstory%2Famp%2Fprigozhin-crash-military-analyst-sean-bell-on-what-the-footage-tells-us-12946365%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fnews.sky.com%2Fstory%2Famp%2Fprigozhin-crash-military-analyst-sean-bell-on-what-the-footage-tells-us-12946365%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Acquitting%20a%20Death-Row%20Convict%2C%20SC%20Lays%20Down%20Guidelines%20on%20Admissibility%20of%20Dying%20Declarations%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cimg%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2018%2F05%2F14145256%2Fgavel_pixabay.jpg%5C%22%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3E%3Cstrong%3ENew%20Delhi%3A%3C%2Fstrong%3E%20The%20Supreme%20Court%2C%20on%20Wednesday%2C%20August%2023%2C%20laid%20down%20elaborate%20and%20clear%20guidelines%20on%20the%20admissibility%20of%20dying%20declarations%20while%20acquitting%20a%20death-row%20convict%20by%20giving%20him%20the%20benefit%20of%20the%20doubt.%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EA%20three-judge%20bench%2C%20comprising%20Justices%20B.R.%20Gavai%2C%20J.B.%20Pardiwala%20and%20Prashant%20Kumar%20Mishra%2C%20in%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fmain.sci.gov.in%2Fsupremecourt%2F2018%2F21899%2F21899_2018_14_1501_46308_Judgement_23-Aug-2023.pdf%5C%22%3E%3Ci%3E%3Cspan%3EIrfan%40Naka%20vs%20the%20State%20of%20Uttar%20Pradesh%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fi%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%20%3Cspan%3Eheld%20that%20the%20court%20should%20always%20be%20on%20guard%20to%20see%20that%20the%20statement%20of%20the%20deceased%20was%20not%20a%20result%20of%20tutoring%20or%20prompting%20or%20a%20product%20of%20imagination.%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EThe%20judgment%2C%20authored%20by%20Justice%20Pardiwala%2C%20came%20in%20a%20case%20in%20which%20a%20resident%20of%20Bijnore%20in%20Uttar%20Pradesh%20was%20convicted%20of%20setting%20his%20son%20and%20two%20brothers%20on%20fire%20while%20they%20were%20sleeping%20%E2%80%93%20because%20of%20personal%20animosity.%20Both%20the%20Bijnore%20additional%20sessions%20judge%20and%20the%20Allahabad%20high%20court%20had%20confirmed%20the%20conviction%20and%20death%20sentence%20of%20the%20appellant-convict.%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EHowever%2C%20the%20top%20court%20concluded%20that%20the%20prosecution%20was%20not%20able%20to%20prove%20beyond%20reasonable%20doubt%20that%20it%20was%20only%20and%20only%20the%20appellant-convict%20who%20set%20the%20room%20on%20fire%20by%20pouring%20an%20inflammable%20substance.%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EBecause%20the%20dying%20declarations%20of%20two%20of%20the%20deceased%20%E2%80%93%20the%20convict%E2%80%99s%20son%20and%20one%20of%20his%20brothers%20%E2%80%93%20played%20a%20crucial%20role%20in%20the%20conviction%2C%20the%20judgment%20dives%20into%20the%20admissibility%20of%20such%20declarations.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EThe%20justification%20for%20the%20sanctity%2Fpresumption%20attached%20to%20a%20dying%20declaration%20is%20two-fold%3A%20First%2C%20ethically%20and%20religiously%20it%20is%20presumed%20that%20a%20person%20while%20at%20the%20brink%20of%20death%20will%20not%20lie%2C%20and%20second%2C%20from%20a%20public%20policy%20perspective%20it%20is%20to%20tackle%20a%20situation%20where%20the%20only%20witness%20to%20the%20crime%20is%20not%20available.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EThe%20bench%20held%20that%20dying%20declarations%2C%20while%20carrying%20a%20presumption%20of%20being%20true%2C%20must%20be%20wholly%20reliable%20and%20inspire%20confidence.%20Where%20there%20is%20any%20suspicion%20over%20the%20veracity%20of%20the%20same%20or%20the%20evidence%20on%20record%20shows%20that%20the%20dying%20declaration%20is%20not%20true%2C%20it%20will%20only%20be%20considered%20as%20a%20piece%20of%20evidence%20but%20cannot%20be%20the%20basis%20for%20conviction%20alone%2C%20it%20added.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EThe%20bench%20clarified%20that%20there%20is%20no%20hard%20and%20fast%20rule%20for%20determining%20when%20a%20dying%20declaration%20should%20be%20accepted.%20The%20duty%20of%20the%20court%20is%20to%20decide%20this%20question%20in%20the%20facts%20and%20surrounding%20circumstances%20of%20the%20case%20and%20be%20fully%20convinced%20of%20the%20truthfulness%20of%20the%20same.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3ECertain%20factors%20can%20be%20considered%20to%20determine%20the%20same%2C%20the%20bench%20held%2C%20adding%20that%20they%20will%20only%20affect%20the%20weight%20of%20the%20dying%20declaration%20and%20not%20its%20admissibility.%20These%20factors%2C%20the%20bench%20said%2C%20are%3A%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cem%3E%3Cspan%3E(i)%20Whether%20the%20person%20making%20the%20statement%20was%20in%20expectation%20of%20death%3F%3Cbr%3E%5Cn%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Cspan%3E(ii)%20Whether%20the%20dying%20declaration%20was%20made%20at%20the%20earliest%20opportunity%3F%20%E2%80%9CRule%20of%20First%20Opportunity%E2%80%9D%3Cbr%3E%5Cn%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Cspan%3E(iii)%20Whether%20there%20is%20any%20reasonable%20suspicion%20to%20believe%20the%20dying%20declaration%20was%20put%20in%20the%20mouth%20of%20the%20dying%20person%3F%3Cbr%3E%5Cn%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Cspan%3E(iv)%20Whether%20the%20dying%20declaration%20was%20a%20product%20of%20prompting%2C%20tutoring%20or%20leading%20at%20the%20instance%20of%20police%20or%20any%20interested%20party%3F%3Cbr%3E%5Cn%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Cspan%3E(v)%20Whether%20the%20statement%20was%20not%20recorded%20properly%3F%3Cbr%3E%5Cn%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Cspan%3E(vi)%20Whether%20the%20dying%20declarant%20had%20the%20opportunity%20to%20clearly%20observe%20the%20incident%3F%3Cbr%3E%5Cn%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Cspan%3E(vii)%20Whether%20the%20dying%20declaration%20has%20been%20consistent%20throughout%3F%3Cbr%3E%5Cn%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Cspan%3E(viii)%20Whether%20the%20dying%20declaration%20in%20itself%20is%20a%20manifestation%2Ffiction%20of%20the%20dying%20person%E2%80%99s%20imagination%20of%20what%20he%20thinks%20transpired%3F%3Cbr%3E%5Cn%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Cspan%3E(ix)%20Whether%20the%20dying%20declaration%20was%20itself%20voluntary%3F%3Cbr%3E%5Cn%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Cspan%3E(x)%20Whether%2C%20as%20per%20the%20injuries%2C%20it%20would%20have%20been%20impossible%20for%20the%20deceased%20to%20make%20a%20dying%20declaration%3F%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EIt%20is%20the%20duty%20of%20the%20prosecution%20to%20establish%20the%20charge%20against%20the%20accused%20beyond%20a%20reasonable%20doubt%3B%20and%20the%20benefit%20of%20doubt%20must%20always%20be%20in%20favour%20of%20the%20accused%2C%20the%20bench%20held.%20It%20is%20true%20that%20a%20dying%20declaration%20is%20a%20substantive%20piece%20of%20evidence%20to%20be%20relied%20on%20%E2%80%93%20provided%20it%20is%20also%20proved%20that%20the%20same%20was%20voluntary%20and%20truthful%20and%20the%20victim%20was%20in%20a%20fit%20state%20of%20mind.%20It%20is%20just%20not%20enough%20for%20the%20court%20to%20say%20that%20the%20dying%20declaration%20is%20reliable%20as%20the%20accused%20is%20named%20in%20the%20dying%20declaration%20as%20the%20assailant%2C%20the%20bench%20explained.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EIt%20is%20unsafe%20to%20record%20the%20conviction%20on%20the%20basis%20of%20a%20dying%20declaration%20alone%20in%20the%20cases%20where%20suspicion%2C%20like%20the%20case%20on%20hand%2C%20is%20raised%2C%20as%20regards%20the%20correctness%20of%20the%20dying%20declaration%2C%20the%20bench%20held.%20In%20such%20cases%2C%20the%20court%20may%20have%20to%20look%20for%20some%20corroborative%20evidence%20by%20treating%20the%20dying%20declaration%20only%20as%20a%20piece%20of%20evidence%3B%20the%20evidence%20and%20material%20available%20on%20record%20must%20be%20properly%20weighed%20in%20each%20case%20to%20arrive%20at%20an%20appropriate%20conclusion%2C%20the%20bench%20clarified.%C2%A0%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3E%E2%80%9CThe%20reason%20why%20we%20say%20so%20is%20that%20in%20the%20case%20on%20hand%2C%20although%20the%20appellant-convict%20was%20named%20in%20two%20dying%20declarations%20as%20the%20person%20who%20set%20the%20room%20on%20fire%2C%20yet%20the%20surrounding%20circumstances%20render%20the%20statements%20of%20the%20declarants%20very%20doubtful%2C%E2%80%9D%20the%20bench%20concluded.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EThe%20judgment%20cites%20the%201974%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Findiankanoon.org%2Fdoc%2F487684%2F%5C%22%3E%3Ci%3E%3Cspan%3EDharam%20Das%20Wadhwani%20vs%20State%20of%20Uttar%20Pradesh%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fi%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%20%3Cspan%3Everdict%20by%20Justice%20Krishna%20Iyer%2C%20which%20held%20that%20the%20rule%20of%20benefit%20of%20reasonable%20doubt%20does%20not%20imply%20a%20frail%20willow%20bending%20to%20every%20whiff%20of%20hesitancy.%20Judges%20are%20made%20of%20sterner%20stuff%20and%20must%20take%20a%20practical%20view%20of%20the%20legitimate%20inferences%20flowing%20from%20the%20evidence%2C%20circumstantial%20or%20direct.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3E%E2%80%9C%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Cspan%3EEven%20applying%20this%20principle%2C%20we%20have%20a%20doubt%20as%20regards%20the%20complicity%20of%20the%20appellant-convict%20in%20the%20crime%2C%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Cspan%3E%E2%80%9D%20the%20order%20by%20Justice%20Pardiwala%20pointed%20out.%C2%A0%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3E%E2%80%9C%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Cspan%3EProsecution%20Witness%5BPW%5D-2%20has%20been%20otherwise%20also%20not%20believed%20by%20the%20High%20Court.%C2%A0%20It%20is%20difficult%20to%20rest%20the%20conviction%20solely%20based%20on%20the%20two%20dying%20declarations.%C2%A0%20The%20oral%20evidence%20of%20the%20PW-4%20Soni%20also%20does%20not%20inspire%20any%20confidence%2C%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Cspan%3E%E2%80%9D%20the%20bench%20further%20added.%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%20class%3D%5C%22wp-caption%5C%22%3E%3Cimg%20sizes%3D%5C%22(max-width%3A%20709px)%2085vw%2C%20(max-width%3A%20909px)%2067vw%2C%20(max-width%3A%201362px)%2062vw%2C%20840px%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F05%2F18150906%2FSupreme-Court.jpg%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20width%3D%5C%221200%5C%22%20srcset%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F05%2F18150906%2FSupreme-Court.jpg%201200w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F05%2F18150906%2FSupreme-Court-300x200.jpg%20300w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F05%2F18150906%2FSupreme-Court-1024x683.jpg%201024w%5C%22%20class%3D%5C%22wp-image-653640%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22800%5C%22%3E%3Cp%20class%3D%5C%22wp-caption-text%5C%22%3EThe%20Supreme%20Court%20of%20India.%20Credit%3A%20Subhashish%20Panigrahi%2FWikimedia%20Commons.%20CC%20by%20SA%204.0%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cb%3EFacts%20of%20the%20case%3C%2Fb%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EThe%20appellant-convict%20was%20married%20twice.%20The%20first%20marriage%20was%20with%20a%20lady%2C%20who%20was%20the%20daughter%20of%20his%20uncle%20(PW-1).%20His%20second%20marriage%20was%20solemnised%20with%20another%20lady.%20One%20son%20by%20the%20name%20of%20Islamuddin%20%E2%80%93%20who%20was%20killed%20in%20the%20fire%20%E2%80%93%20was%20born%20in%20wedlock%20with%20his%20first%20wife.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EThe%20convict%20had%20two%20brothers%2C%20namely%2C%20Irshad%20and%20Naushad%20%E2%80%93%20both%20of%20whom%20were%20also%20killed%20%E2%80%93%20and%20who%20lived%20along%20with%20him%20and%20his%20sister%20Soni%20(PW-4).%20Another%20brother%20by%20the%20name%20Shanu%20alias%20Shahnawaz%20(PW-2)%20of%20the%20convict%20lived%20in%20the%20neighbourhood.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EAccording%20to%20the%20prosecution%2C%20the%20three%20deceased%20persons%20more%20%E2%80%93%20particularly%20Islamuddin%20(the%20convict%E2%80%99s%20son)%20%E2%80%93%20were%20highly%20opposed%20to%20the%20second%20marriage%20of%20the%20appellant-convict.%20Islamuddin%20was%20even%20once%20beaten%20by%20the%20appellant-convict%20as%20he%20had%20offered%20a%20lot%20of%20opposition%20to%20the%20second%20marriage%20of%20his%20father.%20The%20two%20deceased%20brothers%20had%20also%20defended%20Islamuddin%E2%80%99s%20opposition%20to%20the%20second%20marriage%20of%20the%20appellant%2C%20the%20prosecution%20said.%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EOn%20August%206%2C%202014%2C%20at%20around%2012%3A30%20am%2C%20the%20PW-2%20%E2%80%93%20another%20brother%20of%20the%20convict%20%E2%80%93%20is%20said%20to%20have%20woken%20up%20to%20see%20flames%20and%20smoke%20coming%20from%20the%20room%20where%20the%20deceased%20persons%20were%20sleeping.%20The%20PW-2%20and%20his%20sister%20Soni%20(PW-4)%20claim%20to%20have%20seen%20the%20appellant-convict%20setting%20the%20room%20on%20fire%20and%20thereafter%2C%20fastening%20the%20door%20latch%20from%20outside%20and%20running%20away.%20While%20PW-4%20lives%20in%20the%20same%20house%20as%20the%20convict%2C%20PW-2%20claimed%20he%20was%20there%20to%20have%20dinner%20with%20PW-4%20and%20the%20deceased%20persons.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EThe%20prosecution%20claimed%20that%20the%20PW-2%20and%20PW-4%20opened%20their%20doors%20and%20saw%20the%20appellant-convict%20running%20from%20the%20roof%20towards%20the%20stairs.%20According%20to%20the%20case%20of%20the%20prosecution%2C%20two%20other%20persons%20%E2%80%93%20who%20were%20not%20examined%20%E2%80%93%20also%20saw%20the%20appellant-convict%20running%20away.%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%20title%3D%5C%22Page%2023%5C%22%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CWe%20find%20it%20very%20difficult%20to%20believe%20that%20the%20appellant-convict%20was%20still%20inside%20the%20room%20or%20even%20outside%20the%20room%20to%20be%20witnessed%20by%20the%20deceased%20persons%20as%20well%20as%20by%20the%20PW-2%20and%20PW-4%2C%20locking%20the%20room%20from%20outside%20after%20setting%20the%20room%20on%20fire%2C%E2%80%9D%20the%20court%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EAccording%20to%20the%20bench%2C%20the%20conduct%20of%20the%20accused%20might%20be%20%E2%80%9Cunnatural%E2%80%9D%20but%20such%20conduct%2C%20which%20may%20be%20a%20relevant%20factor%20under%20Section%208%20of%20the%20Indian%20Evidence%20Act%20%E2%80%9Cby%20itself%20may%20not%20be%20sufficient%20to%20hold%20a%20person%20guilty%20of%20the%20offence%20of%20murder%E2%80%9D.%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EHad%20the%20dying%20declarations%20stood%20corroborated%20by%20the%20oral%20evidence%20of%20PW-2%20and%20PW-4%2C%20then%20probably%2C%20it%20would%20have%20been%20altogether%20a%20different%20scenario.%20However%2C%20the%20bench%20found%20that%20the%20two%20dying%20declarations%20were%20not%20consistent%20or%20rather%20contradictory%20to%20the%20oral%20evidence%20on%20record.%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1692865771000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2018%2F05%2F14145256%2Fgavel_pixabay.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Flaw%2Fsupreme-court-guidelines-admissibility-dying-declarations%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22A%20three-judge%20bench%20held%20that%20courts%20should%20always%20be%20on%20guard%20to%20see%20that%20the%20statement%20of%20the%20deceased%20was%20not%20a%20result%20of%20tutoring%20or%20prompting%20or%20a%20product%20of%20imagination.%C2%A0%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A2%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Flaw%2Fsupreme-court-guidelines-admissibility-dying-declarations%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Multiple%20Medical%20Tests%20Conducted%20on%20Delhi%20Govt%20Official%20Accused%20of%20Rape%20of%20Minor%20Girl%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cimg%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F08%2F24125734%2FSandeep-Mahajan-1.png%5C%22%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3ENew%20Delhi%3A%C2%A0%3C%2Fstrong%3EThe%20Delhi%20government%20official%20who%20is%20accused%20of%20impregnating%20his%20deceased%20friend%E2%80%99s%20minor%20daughter%20has%20told%20the%20court%20that%20he%20had%20a%20vasectomy%20in%202005.%20He%20has%20been%20made%20to%20take%20several%20tests%20following%20his%20claim.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CTo%20verify%20his%20allegations%2C%20he%20was%20taken%20to%20Lok%20Nayak%20Hospital%20(on%20Tuesday)%2C%20where%20he%20underwent%20a%20series%20of%20medical%20tests.%20These%20included%20a%20potency%20test%2C%20surgical%20manual%20examination%2C%20and%20semen%20analysis%2C%E2%80%9D%20%3Cem%3EIndian%20Express%3C%2Fem%3E%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Findianexpress.com%2Farticle%2Fcities%2Fdelhi%2Fgot-vasectomy-done-in-2005-officer-held-for-rape-tells-court-8906500%2F%5C%22%3Equoted%3C%2Fa%3E%20an%20official%20involved%20in%20the%20investigation%20of%20the%20case.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EWhile%20a%20potency%20test%2C%20which%20is%20a%20procedural%20test%2C%20is%20done%20in%20rape%20cases%20to%20ascertain%20if%20the%20accused%20is%20capable%20of%20engaging%20in%20sexual%20acts%2C%20a%20surgical%20manual%20examination%20is%20carried%20out%20to%20confirm%20if%20the%20vasectomy%20was%20done%20or%20not.%20On%20the%20other%20hand%2C%20semen%20analysis%20is%20carried%20out%20to%20check%20for%20fertility.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20official%20said%20that%20the%20victim%E2%80%99s%20statement%20was%20recorded%20as%20per%20Section%20164%20of%20the%20Code%20of%20Criminal%20Procedure%20(CrPC)%20to%20verify%20her%20allegations%20as%20well%20as%20to%20know%20the%20sequence%20of%20events.%20The%20minor%20is%20being%20counselled%2C%20the%20officer%20added.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20accused%2C%20Premoday%20Khakha%2C%20an%20official%20in%20the%20Delhi%20government%E2%80%99s%20Women%20and%20Child%20Development%20(WCD)%20department%2C%20was%20sent%20to%20a%2014-day%20judicial%20custody%20along%20with%20his%20wife%20Seema%20Rani%20on%20Wednesday%2C%20August%2023.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAs%20per%20the%20first%20information%20report%20(FIR)%2C%20the%20girl%20began%20to%20live%20with%20the%20accused%2C%20whom%20she%20referred%20to%20as%20uncle%2C%20following%20the%20death%20of%20her%20father.%20The%20girl%20said%20that%20she%20moved%20along%20with%20her%20mother%20to%20live%20with%20her%20uncle%20and%20his%20wife%2C%20as%20they%20were%20%E2%80%9Cdepressed%E2%80%9D%20due%20to%20her%20father%E2%80%99s%20death.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CI%20went%20to%20my%20uncle%E2%80%99s%20house%20after%20the%20(father%E2%80%99s)%20death%20to%20divert%20my%20mind%20and%20started%20attending%20online%20classes%20from%20there.%20From%20November%202020%20to%20January%202021%2C%20uncle%20raped%20me%E2%80%A6%20aunty%20was%20strict%20and%20would%20hit%20me%20when%20I%20would%20score%20less%20marks.%20The%20last%20time%20he%20sexually%20assaulted%20me%20was%20in%20January%202021%20and%20then%20I%20missed%20my%20period.%20Aunty%20said%20that%20they%20will%20get%20an%20abortion%20done%20since%20it%E2%80%99s%20the%20first%20month%E2%80%A6%20I%20didn%E2%80%99t%20tell%20my%20mother%20anything%2C%20thinking%20she%20wouldn%E2%80%99t%20believe%20(me).%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%20the%20coming%20days%2C%20the%20police%20will%20question%20the%20family%20of%20the%20accused%20and%20their%20friends%20and%20neighbours.%20The%20police%20so%20far%20have%20prepared%20a%20list%20of%2010%20witnesses%20in%20the%20case.%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1692862152000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F08%2F24125734%2FSandeep-Mahajan-1.png%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fgovernment%2Fmultiple-medical-tests-conducted-on-delhi-govt-official-accused-of-rape-of-minor-girl%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22The%20accused%2C%20Premoday%20Khakha%2C%20an%20official%20in%20the%20Delhi%20government's%20Women%20and%20Child%20Development%20department%2C%20said%20he%20had%20got%20a%20vasectomy%20in%202005.%20He%20has%20been%20made%20to%20take%20several%20tests%20following%20his%20claim.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fgovernment%2Fmultiple-medical-tests-conducted-on-delhi-govt-official-accused-of-rape-of-minor-girl%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Who%20was%20on%20the%20private%20jet%20that%20crashed%20in%20Russia%3F%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%22%2C%22published%22%3A1692862140000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fe3.365dm.com%2F23%2F08%2F768x432%2Fskynews-yevgeny-prigozhin-comp_6261316.jpg%3F20230824154121%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fnews.sky.com%2Fstory%2Fwho-else-was-on-the-russian-private-jet-that-crashed-with-wagner-chief-prigozhin-on-board-12946327%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Ten%20bodies%20have%20been%20recovered%20from%20the%20site%20of%20a%20Russian%20plane%20crash%2C%20state%20media%20has%20said%2C%20with%20a%20number%20of%20high-profile%20members%20of%20the%20Wagner%20mercenary%20group%20reportedly%20on%20board.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A203%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fnews.sky.com%2Fstory%2Fwho-else-was-on-the-russian-private-jet-that-crashed-with-wagner-chief-prigozhin-on-board-12946327%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fnews-sky-com.cdn.ampproject.org%2Fc%2Fs%2Fnews.sky.com%2Fstory%2Famp%2Fwho-else-was-on-the-russian-private-jet-that-crashed-with-wagner-chief-prigozhin-on-board-12946327%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fnews.sky.com%2Fstory%2Famp%2Fwho-else-was-on-the-russian-private-jet-that-crashed-with-wagner-chief-prigozhin-on-board-12946327%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%221984%20Riots%3A%20'Not%20Present%20at%20Crime%20Scene%2C'%20Court%20Drops%20Murder%2C%20Conspiracy%20Charges%20Against%20Sajjan%20Kumar%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cimg%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2018%2F12%2F18160925%2FSajjan1.jpg%5C%22%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3ENew%20Delhi%3A%3C%2Fstrong%3E%20A%20Delhi%20court%20has%20dropped%20charges%20of%20murder%20and%20criminal%20conspiracy%20against%20former%20Congress%20leader%20Sajjan%20Kumar%20in%20two%201984%20riots%20cases.%20It%20has%20framed%20charges%20of%C2%A0rioting%20with%20deadly%20weapons%2C%20promoting%20enmity%20between%20different%20groups%2C%20and%20attempting%20to%20commit%20culpable%20homicide.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cem%3EIndian%20Express%3C%2Fem%3E%20has%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Findianexpress.com%2Farticle%2Fcities%2Fdelhi%2F1984-riots-court-drops-murder-criminal-conspiracy-charges-sajjan-kumar-8906278%2F%5C%22%3Ereported%3C%2Fa%3E%20that%20in%202015%2C%20a%20special%20investigation%20team%20(SIT)%20had%20registered%20two%20FIRs%20against%20Kumar%20based%20on%20complaints%20of%20violence%20in%20Janakpuri%20and%20Vikaspuri%20during%20the%20anti-Sikh%20violence%20of%201984.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThis%20new%20SIT%20had%20been%20formed%20in%202015%2C%20by%20the%20Union%20home%20ministry.%20In%202018%2C%20two%20men%20were%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Ftimesofindia.indiatimes.com%2Fcity%2Fdelhi%2Fa-first-for-sit-two-convicted-for-1984-killings%2Farticleshow%2F66627391.cms%5C%22%3Econvicted%3C%2Fa%3E%20on%20the%20basis%20of%20the%20SIT%E2%80%99s%20investigations%2C%20marking%20the%20first%20arrests%20as%20a%20result%20of%20the%20SIT%E2%80%99s%20probes.%20Sajjan%20Kumar%E2%80%99s%20counsel%20has%20claimed%20in%20court%20that%20the%20formation%20of%20this%20SIT%20is%20illegal.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20Janakpuri%20FIR%20concerned%20the%20deaths%20of%20one%20Sohan%20Singh%20and%20his%20son-in-law%20Avtar%20Singh.%20The%20Vikaspuri%20FIR%20was%20on%20the%20attack%20on%20Gurcharan%20Singh%2C%20who%20was%20set%20ablaze%2C%20sustained%20grievous%20injuries%20and%20remained%20bedridden%20for%20the%20rest%20of%20his%20life.%20These%20incidents%20occurred%20on%20November%201%20and%202%20respectively.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20communal%20violence%20had%20broken%20out%20after%20the%20assassination%20of%20then%20prime%20minister%20Indira%20Gandhi%20on%20October%2031%2C%201984%20by%20her%20two%20Sikh%20bodyguards.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CAllegations%20contained%20in%20this%20consolidated%20chargesheet%2C%20as%20already%20discussed%2C%20do%20not%20make%20out%20a%20prima%20facie%20case%20for%20the%20commission%20of%20the%20offence%20of%20criminal%20conspiracy%2C%E2%80%9D%20the%20Rouse%20Avenue%20court%20said%2C%20according%20to%20%3Cem%3EExpress%3C%2Fem%3E.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20court%20cited%20the%20fact%20that%20Kumar%20was%20not%20present%20at%20the%20scene%20of%20the%20crimes.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%20addition%20to%20rioting%20with%20deadly%20weapons%2C%20promoting%20enmity%20between%20different%20groups%2C%20and%20attempting%20to%20commit%20culpable%20homicide%2C%20Kumar%20was%20also%20charged%20with%20causing%20mischief%20by%20explosive%20substance%20with%20intent%20to%20destroy%20houses.%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1692860436000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2018%2F12%2F18160925%2FSajjan1.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Flaw%2Fsajjan-kumar-1984-riots-murder%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22In%202015%2C%20a%20special%20investigation%20team%20had%20registered%20two%20FIRs%20against%20the%20Congress%20leader%20based%20on%20complaints%20of%20attacks%20in%20Janakpuri%20and%20Vikaspuri%20during%20the%20anti-Sikh%20riots%20of%201984.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A24%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Flaw%2Fsajjan-kumar-1984-riots-murder%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22WFI%20suspended!%20Here's%20why%20global%20wrestling%20body%20revoked%20India's%20membership%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%22%2C%22published%22%3A1692860215000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fbsmedia.business-standard.com%2F_media%2Fbs%2Fimg%2Farticle%2F2023-07%2F27%2Ffull%2F1690448226-3558.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.business-standard.com%2Fsports%2Fasian-game