0Grey%20Zone%C2%A0confirmed%20Prigozhin%E2%80%99s%C2%A0death%2C%20calling%C2%A0him%20a%20hero%20and%20a%20patriot.%20The%20post%20also%20claimed%20he%20had%20died%20at%20the%20hands%20of%20unidentified%20people%20it%20called%20%E2%80%9Ctraitors%20to%20Russia.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CAn%20investigation%20has%20been%20launched%20into%20the%20Embraer%20plane%20crash%20that%20occurred%20tonight%20in%20the%20Tver%20region.%20According%20to%20the%20passenger%20list%2C%20among%20them%20is%20the%20name%20and%20surname%20of%20Yevgeny%20Prigozhin%2C%E2%80%9D%20Rosaviatsia%2C%20the%20Russian%20civil%20aviation%20authority%2C%20said%20regarding%C2%A0the%20plane%E2%80%99s%20crashing.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20jet%20was%20reportedly%20en%20route%20from%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.dw.com%2Fen%2Fmoscow%2Ft-19038132%5C%22%3EMoscow%3C%2Fa%3E%20to%20St.%20Petersburg%20when%20it%20crashed%20near%20the%20village%20of%20Kuzhenkino%20in%20Tver%2C%20a%20region%20over%20100%20kilometres%20north%20of%20the%20Russian%20capital.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20Embraer%20jet%20model%20has%20only%20recorded%20one%20accident%20in%20over%2020%20years%20of%20service%2C%20and%20that%20was%20not%20related%20to%20mechanical%20failure.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%20dir%3D%5C%22ltr%5C%22%3E%E2%80%9CIt%20may%20well%20be%20that%20this%20crash%20was%20not%20a%20tragic%20accident%2C%E2%80%9D%20said%20%3Cem%3EDW%3C%2Fem%3E%20Russia%20bureau%20chief%20Juri%20Rescheto.%20%E2%80%9CHe%20became%20very%20important%20for%20the%20Kremlin.%20He%20became%20so%20powerful%20he%20was%20extremely%20inconvenient%20and%20dared%20to%20publicly%20and%20loudly%20doubt%20the%20sense%20of%20the%20war%20in%20Ukraine.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%20dir%3D%5C%22ltr%5C%22%3EIf%20Prigozhin%E2%80%99s%C2%A0death%20is%20confirmed%2C%20%E2%80%9CI%20can%20imagine%20that%20the%20Wagner%20Group%20will%20no%20longer%20exist%20as%20a%20fighting%20force%2C%E2%80%9D%20Rescheto%20added.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThere%20have%20been%20many%20questions%20about%20Prigozhin%E2%80%99s%C2%A0whereabouts%20since%20he%20led%20his%20mercenary%20soldiers%20on%20a%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.dw.com%2Fen%2Fyevgeny-prigozhins-mutiny-a-stress-test-for-vladimir-putin%2Fa-66048426%5C%22%3Eshort-lived%20mutiny%20against%20Moscow%3C%2Fa%3E%20on%20June%2023.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EA%20video%2C%20allegedly%20of%20Prigozhin%2C%20was%20released%20just%20two%20days%20ago%20on%20Telegram%20and%20appeared%20to%20show%20him%20in%20Africa.%20It%20would%20be%20his%20first%20video%20since%20the%20abandoned%20mutiny.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EWhite%20House%3A%20Prigozhin%E2%80%99s%20death%20%E2%80%98no%20surprise%E2%80%99%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20White%20House%20also%20acknowledged%C2%A0the%20news%20and%20President%C2%A0Joe%20Biden%20spoke%20with%20reporters%20candidly%20on%20the%20matter%20as%20he%20was%20leaving%20a%20fitness%20studio%2C%20while%20on%20vacation.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CI%20don%E2%80%99t%20know%20for%20a%20fact%20what%20happened%2C%20but%20I%E2%80%99m%20not%20surprised%2C%E2%80%9D%20Biden%20said%2C%20adding%2C%20%E2%80%9Cthere%E2%80%99s%20not%20much%20that%20happens%20in%20Russia%20that%20(President)%20Putin%E2%80%99s%20not%20behind.%20But%20I%20don%E2%80%99t%20know%20enough%20to%20know%20the%20answer.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EMykhailo%20Podolyak%2C%20Ukrainian%20presidential%20adviser%2C%20reacted%20to%20the%20news%C2%A0on%20the%20social%20media%20platform%20X%2C%20formerly%20known%20as%20Twitter%2C%20saying%20it%20was%20%E2%80%9Cobvious%E2%80%9D%20Putin%20would%20make%20an%20example%20of%C2%A0Prigozhin.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CThe%20demonstrative%20elimination%20of%20Prigozhin%20and%20the%20Wagner%20command%20two%20months%20after%20the%20coup%20attempt%20is%20a%20signal%20from%20Putin%20to%20Russia%E2%80%99s%20elites%20ahead%20of%20the%202024%20elections%2C%E2%80%9D%C2%A0Podolyak%20added.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3C