40nativeorganics.nagaland)%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3C%2Fblockquote%3E%20%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%20Nagaland%2C%20Dr%20Longkumer%20is%20something%20of%20a%20hero.%20His%20startup%20Konger%20Agritech%20has%20spent%20the%20years%20since%20its%20inception%20training%20over%20500%20farmers%20in%20Nagaland%20in%20shiitake%20and%20oyster%20mushroom%20cultivation%20and%20generated%20%E2%80%9Capproximately%2020%2C00%2C000%20Shiitake%20dowel%20spawns%20and%2025%2C000%20kg%20of%20Oyster%20mushroom%20spawns%E2%80%9D.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch2%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-heading%5C%22%3EWhy%20shiitake%20mushrooms%3F%3C%2Fh2%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EPrior%20to%202018%2C%20Government-backed%20laboratories%20produced%20the%20fungi%20only%20during%20the%20winter%20months%20%E2%80%94%20a%20reality%20that%20Dr%20Longkumer%20attempted%20to%20change%20with%20his%20startup.%20He%20wanted%20to%20ensure%20the%20perennial%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thebetterindia.com%2F270722%2Fmushroom-farming-startup-vedanta-makes-healthy-food%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Eavailability%20of%20these%20mushrooms%20%3C%2Fa%3Eand%20pass%20on%20the%20information%20on%20how%20to%20cultivate%20them%20to%20farmers%20in%20the%20state.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ELh%C3%BCvevol%C3%BC%20was%20one%20of%20the%20lucky%20recipients.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAs%20she%20recounts%2C%20%E2%80%9CDr%20Longkumer%20helped%20me%20out%20tirelessly%20and%20taught%20me%20the%20ways%20of%20cultivating%20mushrooms.%20Besides%2C%20I%20also%20wanted%20to%20try%20growing%20a%20mushroom%20that%20was%20in%20demand%2C%20tasted%20really%20good%2C%20had%20medicinal%20benefits%2C%20and%20could%20be%20cultivated%20in%20our%20type%20of%20environment.%20So%20I%20settled%20on%20the%20idea%20of%20shiitake%20since%20the%20production%20was%20easier%20and%20simpler%20in%20comparison%20to%20other%20mushrooms.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThese%20mushrooms%20come%20with%20a%20host%20of%20benefits.%20The%20dark%20brown%20fungi