%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Elost%20children%20%3C%2Fa%3Ein%20Varanasi%20have%20been%20reunited%20with%20their%20families%20since%20last%20July.%20This%20could%20have%20been%20possible%20with%20Mission%20Muskaan%2C%20supervised%20by%20IAS%20officer%20Himanshu%20Nagpal.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch2%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-heading%5C%22%3EGiving%20happiness%20back%20to%20families%3C%2Fh2%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EOriginally%20hailing%20from%20the%20Hissar%20district%20of%20Haryana%2C%20Himanshu%20is%20a%202019-batch%20IAS%20officer.%20Last%20year%2C%20he%20was%20posted%20as%20the%20Chief%20Development%20Officer%20(CDO)%20in%20Varanasi.%20During%20a%20field%20visit%2C%20he%20came%20across%20a%20few%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thebetterindia.com%2F307058%2Futtarakhand-dgp-ashok-kumar-rehabilitates-child-beggars-with-education-operation-mukti%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Echildren%20begging%3C%2Fa%3E%20at%20a%20circle.%20After%20speaking%20to%20them%2C%20he%20found%20that%20the%20children%20had%20been%20living%20under%20the%20flyover%20and%20were%20not%20from%20the%20city.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CThousands%20of%20tourists%20visit%20Kashi%20city%20every%20day.%20At%20times%2C%20children%20coming%20along%20with%20their%20parents%20are%20lost%2C%20and%20then%20they%20have%20to%20turn%20to%20begging%20to%20fend%20for%20themselves.%20We%20found%20many%20such%20children%20at%20railway%20stations%2C%20temples%2C%20and%20the%20%3Cem%3Eghats%3C%2Fem%3E.%20Some%20of%20these%20children%20have%20been%20here%20for%20as%20long%20as%20five%20years%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20tells%20%3Cstrong%3EThe%20Better%20India%3C%2Fstrong%3E.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-image%5C%22%3E%5Cn%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20sizes%3D%5C%22(max-width%3A%201200px)%20100vw%2C%201200px%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F08%2Fmission-muskaan-1691757485.jpg%5C%22%20width%3D%5C%221200%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22After%20i